26 EveRobotAgent::EveRobotAgent()
27 : Node("eve_robot_agent")
28 {
29  monitoring_data_.brake_source.clear();
30  last_motor_brake_ = false;
31  last_tof_brake_ = false;
32  last_monitoring_pub_time = now();
33  // declare parameters and
34  RCLCPP_INFO(get_logger(), "Node started!");
35  using namespace std::chrono_literals;
36  callback_group_robot_ =
37  create_callback_group(rclcpp::CallbackGroupType::MutuallyExclusive);
38  callback_group_inner_service_ =
39  create_callback_group(rclcpp::CallbackGroupType::MutuallyExclusive);
40  callback_group_gaemi_server_ =
41  create_callback_group(rclcpp::CallbackGroupType::MutuallyExclusive);
42  status_check_ = create_callback_group(rclcpp::CallbackGroupType::MutuallyExclusive);
43  if (load_parameters() == true) {
44  RCLCPP_INFO(get_logger(), "load parameters success");
45  logger_setup();
46  if (get_agent_netinfo(eth_ifr_) == true) {
47  init_ros_publisher();
48  init_ros_subscriber_hw();
49  init_sensor_subscriber();
50  init_ros_subscriber_sw();
51  init_task_subscriber();
52  init_ros_srv_client();
53  init_ros_srv_server(robot_serial_);
54  // TF Listener
55  tf_buffer_ = std::make_shared<tf2_ros::Buffer>(this->get_clock());
56  tf_listener_ = std::make_shared<tf2_ros::TransformListener>(*tf_buffer_);
57  // create timer for period work
58  // initialize control status to stopped
59  monitoring_data_.traffic_wait = false;
60  is_control_ = STOPPED;
61  is_traffic_control_ = false;
62  target_robot_ = "";
63  user_id_.clear();
64  error_status_flag_ = false;
65  timer_ = create_wall_timer(
66  200ms, std::bind(
67  &EveRobotAgent::timer_callback,
68  this), status_check_);
69  pub_started_service();
70  } else {
71  RCLCPP_WARN_STREAM(get_logger(), "Failed to get_agent_netinfo");
72  }
73  }
74  sync_setup();
75  start_maintenance_check();
76  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(get_logger(), "public_ip : " << utils.get_public_ip());
77  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(get_logger(), "init complet");
78 // std::cout << utils.kill_process("demo_nodes_cpp") << "wow";
79 }
80 
81 EveRobotAgent::~EveRobotAgent()
82 {
83  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(get_logger(), "Node destroy....");
84 }

86 
87 void EveRobotAgent::timer_callback()
88 {
89 // pub_monitoring_data();
90 // RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(get_logger(), "timer callback 1hz");
91  if (monitoring_data_.docked_status == true) {
92  if (docked_10s_cnt_ % 50 == 0) {
93  pub_monitoring_data();
94  }
95  docked_10s_cnt_++;
96  } else {
97  docked_10s_cnt_ = 0;
98  pub_monitoring_data();
99  }
100 }
101 
102 bool EveRobotAgent::get_agent_netinfo(std::string eth_ifr_)
103 {
104  std::lock_guard<std::mutex> lock(mutex_);
105  try {
106  net_info = utils.get_net_info(eth_ifr_);
107  if (net_info.ip_addr_ == "Unknown" || net_info.mac_addr_ == "Unknown") {
108  return false;
109  }
110  started_data_.ip = net_info.ip_addr_;
111  started_data_.mac_addr = net_info.mac_addr_;
112  heartbeat_data_.mac_addr = net_info.mac_addr_;
113  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(get_logger(), "Robot IP : " << started_data_.ip);
114  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(get_logger(), "Robot MAC : " << started_data_.mac_addr);
115  return true;
116  } catch (std::exception e) {
117  RCLCPP_WARN_STREAM(get_logger(), "Get Agent Info Exception : " << e.what());
118  return false;
119  }
120 }
121 
122 bool EveRobotAgent::logger_setup()
123 {
124  try {
125  std::string logger_section = "logger";
126  this->declare_parameter<bool>(
127  logger_section + ".capture", true);
128  this->get_parameter<bool>(
129  logger_section + ".capture", capture_);
130  std::string home = std::string(getenv("HOME"));
131  default_file_path = home + "/eve_log";
132  DIR * dir = opendir(default_file_path.c_str());
133  if (dir) {
134  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(get_logger(), "Directory exists : " << default_file_path);
135  } else if (ENOENT == errno) {
136  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(get_logger(), "make dir : " << default_file_path);
137  mkdir(default_file_path.c_str(), 0777);
138  } else {
139  RCLCPP_ERROR_STREAM(get_logger(), "opendir() failed for some other reason.");
140  }
141  closedir(dir);
142 
143  default_cap_file_path = default_file_path + "/cap";
144  dir = opendir(default_cap_file_path.c_str());
145  if (dir) {
146  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(get_logger(), "Directory exists : " << default_cap_file_path);
147  } else if (ENOENT == errno) {
148  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(get_logger(), "make dir : " << default_cap_file_path);
149  mkdir(default_cap_file_path.c_str(), 0777);
150  } else {
151  RCLCPP_ERROR_STREAM(get_logger(), "opendir() failed for some other reason.");
152  }
153  closedir(dir);
154 
155  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(get_logger(), "default_file_path : " << default_file_path);
156  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(get_logger(), "default_cap_file_path : " << default_cap_file_path);
157  return true;
158  } catch (std::exception e) {
159  return false;
160  }
161 }
162 
163 bool EveRobotAgent::transform_pose(
164  geometry_msgs::msg::PoseStamped origin_pose,
165  std::string refer_frame_id,
166  geometry_msgs::msg::PoseStamped * transformed_pose)
167 {
168  try {
169  geometry_msgs::msg::TransformStamped distance_transform;
170  distance_transform = tf_buffer_->lookupTransform(
171  origin_pose.header.frame_id, refer_frame_id,
172  rclcpp::Time(0), rclcpp::Duration::from_seconds(0.5));
173  // request->reference.stamp, rclcpp::Duration::from_seconds(0.5));
174  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(
175  this->get_logger(), "TF is (" <<
176  distance_transform.transform.translation.x << ", " <<
177  distance_transform.transform.translation.y << ", " <<
178  atan2(
179  distance_transform.transform.rotation.z,
180  distance_transform.transform.rotation.w) * 360.0 / M_PI <<
181  ")");
182 
183  tf2::Transform tf_to_refer_frame;
184  tf_to_refer_frame.setOrigin(
185  tf2::Vector3(
186  distance_transform.transform.translation.x,
187  distance_transform.transform.translation.y,
188  distance_transform.transform.translation.z));
189  tf_to_refer_frame.setRotation(
190  tf2::Quaternion(
191  distance_transform.transform.rotation.x,
192  distance_transform.transform.rotation.y,
193  distance_transform.transform.rotation.z,
194  distance_transform.transform.rotation.w));
195 
196  tf2::Transform origin_tf;
197  origin_tf.setOrigin(
198  tf2::Vector3(
199  origin_pose.pose.position.x,
200  origin_pose.pose.position.y,
201  origin_pose.pose.position.z));
202  origin_tf.setRotation(
203  tf2::Quaternion(
204  origin_pose.pose.orientation.x,
205  origin_pose.pose.orientation.y,
206  origin_pose.pose.orientation.z,
207  origin_pose.pose.orientation.w));
208 
209  auto new_pose = tf_to_refer_frame.inverse() * origin_tf;
210  // Stamp
211  transformed_pose->header.stamp = distance_transform.header.stamp;
212  transformed_pose->header.frame_id = refer_frame_id;
213  transformed_pose->pose.position.x = new_pose.getOrigin().x();
214  transformed_pose->pose.position.y = new_pose.getOrigin().y();
215  transformed_pose->pose.position.z = new_pose.getOrigin().z();
216  transformed_pose->pose.orientation.w = new_pose.getRotation().w();
217  transformed_pose->pose.orientation.x = new_pose.getRotation().x();
218  transformed_pose->pose.orientation.y = new_pose.getRotation().y();
219  transformed_pose->pose.orientation.z = new_pose.getRotation().z();
220  } catch (tf2::TransformException & ex) {
221  RCLCPP_WARN_STREAM(
222  this->get_logger(),
223  "Failed to get the TF, so the Pose relative to map_current is returned. : " << ex.what());
224  return false;
225  }
226  return true;
227 }

229 bool EveRobotAgent::load_parameters()
230 {
231  try {
232  this->declare_parameter<std::string>("robot_serial", "");
233  robot_serial_ = this->get_parameter("robot_serial").as_string();
234  this->declare_parameter<std::string>("service_site", "");
235  service_site_ = this->get_parameter("service_site").as_string();
236  started_data_.site_id = service_site_;
237  started_data_.mac_addr = mac_addr_;
238  started_data_.ip = ip_addr_;
239  activity_result_data_.site_id = service_site_;
240  activity_result_data_.robot_serial = robot_serial_;
241  monitoring_data_.robot_serial = robot_serial_;
242  monitoring_data_.site_id = service_site_;
243  heartbeat_data_.robot_serial = robot_serial_;
244  started_data_.robot_serial = robot_serial_;
245  task_status_data_.robot_serial = robot_serial_;
246  changed_config_data_.robot_serial = robot_serial_;
247  is_maintenance_mode_ = read_maintenance_mode_file();
248  this->declare_parameter<std::string>("net_adapter", "enx00c201709576");
249  eth_ifr_ = this->get_parameter("net_adapter").as_string();
250  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(get_logger(), "Robot serial number : " << robot_serial_);
251  this->declare_parameter<std::vector<std::string>>(
252  "ultrasonic_list",
253  std::vector<std::string>());
254  ultrasonic_list_ = this->get_parameter("ultrasonic_list").as_string_array();
255  RCLCPP_WARN_STREAM(get_logger(), "size : " << ultrasonic_list_.size());
256  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(get_logger(), "sonic : " << ultrasonic_list_.at(1));
257  size_t num_of_ultrasonic = ultrasonic_list_.size();
258  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(get_logger(), "sonic : " << num_of_ultrasonic);
259  ultrasonic_angle_.resize(num_of_ultrasonic);
260  ultrasonic_topic_name_.resize(num_of_ultrasonic);
261  ultrasonic_sub_.resize(num_of_ultrasonic);
262  for (size_t i = 0; i < num_of_ultrasonic; i++) {
263  this->declare_parameter<double>(ultrasonic_list_.at(i) + "." + "angle", 0.0);
264  ultrasonic_angle_.at(i) =
265  static_cast<float>(this->get_parameter(ultrasonic_list_.at(i) + "." + "angle").as_double());
266  RCLCPP_WARN_STREAM(get_logger(), "angle " << ultrasonic_angle_.at(i));
267  this->declare_parameter<std::string>(ultrasonic_list_.at(i) + "." + "ros_msg", "");
268  ultrasonic_topic_name_.at(i) =
269  this->get_parameter(ultrasonic_list_.at(i) + "." + "ros_msg").as_string();
270  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(get_logger(), "sonic : " << ultrasonic_topic_name_.at(i).c_str());
271  RCLCPP_WARN_STREAM(get_logger(), "name of topic " << ultrasonic_topic_name_.at(i));
272  }
273  // navi
274  std::string nav_section_name = "navigation";
275  this->declare_parameter<std::string>(
276  nav_section_name + ".navigation_goal_action", "/navigate_to_pose");
277  this->declare_parameter<std::string>(
278  nav_section_name + ".compute_path_action", "/compute_path_to_pose");
279  this->declare_parameter<std::string>(
280  nav_section_name + ".initial_pose_topic", "/compute_path_to_pose");
281  this->declare_parameter<std::vector<std::string>>(
282  nav_section_name + ".clear_costmap_service",
283  {"/local_costmap/clear_entirely_local_costmap",
284  "/global_costmap/clear_entirely_global_costmap"});
285 
286  this->get_parameter<std::string>(
287  nav_section_name + ".navigation_goal_action", navigation_goal_action_);
288  this->get_parameter<std::string>(
289  nav_section_name + ".compute_path_action", compute_path_action_);
290  this->get_parameter<std::vector<std::string>>(
291  nav_section_name + ".clear_costmap_service", clear_costmap_services_);
292  this->get_parameter<std::string>(
293  nav_section_name + ".initial_pose_topic", initial_pose_topic_);
294  // service
295  std::string tree_name = "tree_name";
296  this->declare_parameter<std::string>(
297  tree_name + ".back_to_base_tree_name", back_to_base_tree_name_);
298  this->declare_parameter<std::string>(
299  tree_name + ".move_goal_tree_name", move_goal_tree_name_);
300  this->declare_parameter<std::string>(
301  tree_name + ".back_to_customer_tree_name", back_to_customer_tree_name_);
302  this->declare_parameter<std::string>(
303  tree_name + ".move_to_customer_tree_name", move_to_customer_tree_name_);
304  this->declare_parameter<std::string>(
305  tree_name + ".go_into_ev_tree_name", go_into_ev_tree_name_);
306  this->declare_parameter<std::string>(
307  tree_name + ".go_out_of_ev_tree_name", go_out_of_ev_tree_name_);
308  this->declare_parameter<std::string>(
309  tree_name + ".serve_customer_tree_name", serve_customer_tree_name_);
310  this->declare_parameter<std::string>(
311  tree_name + ".knock_tree_name", knock_tree_name_);
312  this->declare_parameter<std::string>(
313  tree_name + ".transfer_input_tree_name", transfer_input_tree_name_);
314  this->declare_parameter<std::string>(
315  tree_name + ".docent_tree_name", docent_tree_name_);
316  this->declare_parameter<std::string>(

320  this->declare_parameter<std::string>(

322  this->get_parameter<std::string>(

409 void EveRobotAgent::init_ros_publisher()
410 {
411  const auto QOS_PROFILE = rclcpp::QoS(rclcpp::KeepLast(20)).reliable().transient_local();
412  monitoring_data_.ultrasonic_angle.resize(ultrasonic_list_.size());
413  monitoring_data_.ultrasonic_range.resize(ultrasonic_list_.size());
414  monitoring_data_.lidar_angle.clear();
415  monitoring_data_.lidar_range.clear();
416  monitoring_data_pub_ =
417  create_publisher<eve_server_interfaces::msg::MonitoringData>(
418  robot_serial_ + "/eve_server/monitoring_data", 0);
419  heartbeat_pub_ =
420  create_publisher<eve_server_interfaces::msg::Heartbeat>(
421  robot_serial_ + "/eve_server/heartbeat",
422  0);
423 
424  activity_result_pub_ = create_publisher<eve_server_interfaces::msg::ActivityResult>(
425  robot_serial_ + "/eve_server/activity_result", 0);
426 
427  started_pub_ =
428  create_publisher<eve_server_interfaces::msg::Started>(
429  robot_serial_ + "/eve_server/started", 0);
430 
431  task_result_pub_ = create_publisher<eve_server_interfaces::msg::TaskResult>(
432  robot_serial_ + "/eve_server/task_result", QOS_PROFILE);
433 
434 
435  task_status_pub_ = create_publisher<eve_server_interfaces::msg::TaskStatus>(
436  robot_serial_ + "/eve_server/task_status", 0);
437 
438  changed_config_pub_ = create_publisher<eve_server_interfaces::msg::ChangedConfigValue>(
439  robot_serial_ + "/eve_server/changed_config_value", 0);
440 
441  set_gui_info_data_pub_ = create_publisher<std_msgs::msg::String>(
442  "/set_gui_info", QOS_PROFILE);
443 
444  server_log_pub_ = create_publisher<eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log>(
445  robot_serial_ + "/eve_server/log", QOS_PROFILE);
446 
447  ev_status_array_pub_ = create_publisher<eve_server_interfaces::msg::EvStatusArray>(
448  robot_serial_ + "/eve_server/ev_status_array", QOS_PROFILE);
449 
450  cargo_lock_pub_ = create_publisher<aimbot_hw_interfaces::msg::CargoUnlockCmd>(
451  "/aimbot_base/cargo_lock_cmd", QOS_PROFILE);
452 
453  cargo_unlock_pub_ = create_publisher<aimbot_hw_interfaces::msg::CargoUnlockCmd>(
454  "/aimbot_base/cargo_unlock_cmd", QOS_PROFILE);
455 
456  init_pose_pub_ = create_publisher<geometry_msgs::msg::PoseWithCovarianceStamped>(
457  "/initialpose", QOS_PROFILE);
458 
459  simple_path_stop_pub_ = create_publisher<std_msgs::msg::Empty>(
460  "/target_2d_stop", QOS_PROFILE);
461 
462 
463  server_noti_pub_ = create_publisher<eve_server_interfaces::msg::Notify>(
464  robot_serial_ + "/eve_server/notify", QOS_PROFILE);
465 
466  app_noti_pub_ = create_publisher<robotis_server_interfaces::msg::AppNotify>(
467  "/app_notipy", QOS_PROFILE);
468 
469  task_command_pub_ = create_publisher<std_msgs::msg::Int8>(
470  "/service_manager/task_command", QOS_PROFILE);
471 }
472 
473 void EveRobotAgent::sync_setup()
474 {
475  using namespace std::placeholders;
476  using Lidar = sensor_msgs::msg::LaserScan;
477  using Mani = sensor_msgs::msg::JointState;
478  using Mstate = aimbot_state_interfaces::msg::MotionState;
479 // message_filters::Subscriber<sensor_msgs::msg::LaserScan> msg_lidar_sub_;
480 // message_filters::Subscriber<sensor_msgs::msg::JointState> msg_mani_joint_sub_;
481 // message_filters::Subscriber<aimbot_state_interfaces::msg::MotionState> msg_state_sub_;
482  rmw_qos_profile_t custom_qos_profile = rmw_qos_profile_default;
483  custom_qos_profile.depth = 1;
484  custom_qos_profile.reliability =
485  rmw_qos_reliability_policy_t::RMW_QOS_POLICY_RELIABILITY_BEST_EFFORT;
486  custom_qos_profile.history = rmw_qos_history_policy_t::RMW_QOS_POLICY_HISTORY_KEEP_LAST;
487  custom_qos_profile.durability =
488  rmw_qos_durability_policy_t::RMW_QOS_POLICY_DURABILITY_TRANSIENT_LOCAL;
489  msg_lidar_sub_ = std::make_shared<message_filters::Subscriber<sensor_msgs::msg::LaserScan>>(
490  this,
491  "/scan");
492 
493  msg_mani_joint_sub_ = std::make_shared<message_filters::Subscriber<sensor_msgs::msg::JointState>>(
494  this, "/gc_manipulator/joint_states");
495 
496  msg_state_sub_ =
497  std::make_shared<message_filters::Subscriber<aimbot_state_interfaces::msg::MotionState>>(
498  this,
499  "/motion_state");
500 
501  topic_sync_ = std::make_shared<message_filters::TimeSynchronizer<Lidar, Mani, Mstate>>(
502  *msg_lidar_sub_, *msg_mani_joint_sub_, *msg_state_sub_, 10);
503 
504  topic_sync_->registerCallback(&EveRobotAgent::full_sync_topic, this);
505  topic_sync_->registerDropCallback(&EveRobotAgent::drop_topic, this);
506 }

524 void EveRobotAgent::init_ros_subscriber_sw()
525 {
526  auto sub_opt_gaemi_server_cbgroup = rclcpp::SubscriptionOptions();
527  sub_opt_gaemi_server_cbgroup.callback_group = callback_group_gaemi_server_;
528 
529  auto sub_opt_robot_cbgroup = rclcpp::SubscriptionOptions();
530  sub_opt_robot_cbgroup.callback_group = callback_group_robot_;
531 
532  changed_config_value_sub_ =
533  create_subscription<robotis_server_interfaces::msg::ChangedConfigValue>(
534  "/aimbot_base/changed_config_value", rclcpp::SystemDefaultsQoS(),
535  [this](const robotis_server_interfaces::msg::ChangedConfigValue::SharedPtr msg) -> void {
536  changed_config_data_.volume = msg->volume;
537  changed_config_data_.password = msg->password;
538  changed_config_data_.language = msg->language;
539  changed_config_pub_->publish(changed_config_data_);
540  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(get_logger(), "Published change config data!");
541  }, sub_opt_robot_cbgroup);
542 
543 
544  notify_sub_ = create_subscription<robotis_server_interfaces::msg::FmsNotify>(
545  "/fms_notify", rclcpp::SystemDefaultsQoS(),
546  [this](const robotis_server_interfaces::msg::FmsNotify::SharedPtr msg) -> void {
547 // if (msg->app_alarm == true) {
548 // app_noti_pub(*msg);
549 // }
550  publish_server_noti(*msg);
551  }, sub_opt_robot_cbgroup);
552 
553  task_seq_sub_ = create_subscription<task_manager_interfaces::msg::TaskSequence>(
554  "/present_task_sequence", rclcpp::SystemDefaultsQoS(),
555  [this](const task_manager_interfaces::msg::TaskSequence::SharedPtr msg) -> void
556  {
557  std::lock_guard<std::mutex> lock(
558  mutex_);
559  switch (msg->sequence) {
560  case task_manager_interfaces::msg::TaskSequence::START:
561  this->monitoring_data_.present_task_sequence =
562  eve_server_interfaces::msg::MonitoringData::DEPARTED;
563  break;
564  case task_manager_interfaces::msg::TaskSequence::EV_WAIT:
565  this->monitoring_data_.present_task_sequence =
566  eve_server_interfaces::msg::MonitoringData::EV_WAIT;
567  break;
568  case task_manager_interfaces::msg::TaskSequence::EV_GO_INSIDE:
569  this->monitoring_data_.present_task_sequence =
570  eve_server_interfaces::msg::MonitoringData::EV_GO_INSIDE;
571  break;
572  case task_manager_interfaces::msg::TaskSequence::EV_MOVING:
573  this->monitoring_data_.present_task_sequence =
574  eve_server_interfaces::msg::MonitoringData::EV_MOVING;
575  break;
576  case task_manager_interfaces::msg::TaskSequence::EV_GO_OUTSIDE:
577  this->monitoring_data_.present_task_sequence =
578  eve_server_interfaces::msg::MonitoringData::EV_GO_OUTSIDE;
579  break;
580  case task_manager_interfaces::msg::TaskSequence::MOVE_TO_GOAL:
581  this->monitoring_data_.present_task_sequence =
582  eve_server_interfaces::msg::MonitoringData::MOVE_TO_GOAL;
583  break;
584  case task_manager_interfaces::msg::TaskSequence::ARRIVED:
585  this->monitoring_data_.present_task_sequence =
586  eve_server_interfaces::msg::MonitoringData::ARRIVED;
587  break;
588  case task_manager_interfaces::msg::TaskSequence::LAST_ACTION:
589  this->monitoring_data_.present_task_sequence =
590  eve_server_interfaces::msg::MonitoringData::LAST_ACTION;
591  break;
592  case task_manager_interfaces::msg::TaskSequence::FINISH:
593  this->monitoring_data_.present_task_sequence =
594  eve_server_interfaces::msg::MonitoringData::FINISH;
595  break;
596  }
597  }, sub_opt_robot_cbgroup);
598 
599  // gui_current_page_sub
600  current_gui_page_info_sub_ = create_subscription<std_msgs::msg::String>(
601  "/aimbot_base/curr_gui_page", rclcpp::SystemDefaultsQoS(),
602  [this](const std_msgs::msg::String::SharedPtr msg) -> void
603  {
604  std::lock_guard<std::mutex> lock(mutex_);
605  this->monitoring_data_.current_gui_page = msg->data;
606  }, sub_opt_robot_cbgroup);
607 
608  // detected_door_polygon_sub
609  detected_door_sub_ = create_subscription<geometry_msgs::msg::PolygonStamped>(
610  "/door_polygon", rclcpp::SystemDefaultsQoS(),
611  [this](const geometry_msgs::msg::PolygonStamped::SharedPtr msg) -> void
612  {
613  std::lock_guard<std::mutex> lock(mutex_);
614  this->monitoring_data_.detected_door.clear();
615  for (const auto & point : msg->polygon.points) {
616  if (point.z == 0.0) {
617  this->monitoring_data_.detected_door.push_back(point);
618  }
619  }
620  }, sub_opt_robot_cbgroup);
621 
622  // robot log sub
623  robot_log_sub_ = create_subscription<aimbot_log_interfaces::msg::Log>(
624  "/aimbot_log", rclcpp::SystemDefaultsQoS(),
625  [this](const aimbot_log_interfaces::msg::Log::SharedPtr msg) -> void
626  {
627  std::lock_guard<std::mutex> lock(mutex_);
628  write_log_file(*msg);
629  server_log_data_.robot_serial = robot_serial_;
630  server_log_data_.site_id = service_site_;
631  server_log_data_.header = msg->header;
632  switch (msg->level) {
633  case aimbot_log_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_LOW:
634  server_log_data_.level = eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_LOW;
635  break;
636  case aimbot_log_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_MEDIUM:
637  server_log_data_.level = eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_MEDIUM;
638  break;
639  case aimbot_log_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_HIGH:
640  server_log_data_.level = eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_HIGH;
641  break;
642  case aimbot_log_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_DEBUG:
643  server_log_data_.level = eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_DEBUG;
644  break;
645  }
646  switch (msg->type) {
647  case aimbot_log_interfaces::msg::Log::TYPE_INFO:
648  server_log_data_.type = eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::TYPE_INFO;
649  break;
650  case aimbot_log_interfaces::msg::Log::TYPE_WARN:
651  server_log_data_.type = eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::TYPE_WARN;
652  break;
653  case aimbot_log_interfaces::msg::Log::TYPE_ERROR:
654  server_log_data_.type = eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::TYPE_ERROR;
655  break;
656  }
657  server_log_data_.charging_status = battery_status_;
658  server_log_data_.source = msg->source;
659  server_log_data_.contents = msg->contents;
660  server_log_data_.target_poi = msg->target_poi;
661  server_log_data_.battery_percentage = monitoring_data_.battery_percentage;
662  server_log_data_.battery_voltage = static_cast<double>(battery_state_data_.voltage) * 1e-2;
663  server_log_data_.capture = msg->capture;
664  server_log_data_.pose_from_map_current.x = monitoring_data_.pose_from_map_current.x;
665  server_log_data_.pose_from_map_current.y = monitoring_data_.pose_from_map_current.y;
666  server_log_data_.pose_from_map_current.theta = monitoring_data_.pose_from_map_current.theta;
667  server_log_data_.floor = monitoring_data_.area_id;
668  server_log_pub_->publish(server_log_data_);
669  }, sub_opt_robot_cbgroup);
670 }

672 // NOLINT
673 void EveRobotAgent::init_task_subscriber()
674 {
675  auto sub_opt_robot_cbgroup = rclcpp::SubscriptionOptions();
676  sub_opt_robot_cbgroup.callback_group = callback_group_robot_;
677  // task list
678  task_list_sub_ = create_subscription<task_manager_interfaces::msg::TaskListItems>(
679  "/service_manager/task_list", rclcpp::SystemDefaultsQoS(),
680  [this](const task_manager_interfaces::msg::TaskListItems::SharedPtr msg) -> void
681  {
682  std::lock_guard<std::mutex> lock(mutex_);
683  this->task_list_ = *msg;
684  this->task_status_data_.tasks.clear();
685  this->monitoring_data_.tasks.clear();
686  // if (msg->tasks.size() == 0) {
687  // this->monitoring_data_.present_task_sequence = "";
688  // }
689  // check task status
690  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(get_logger(), "task_list_sub_callback_excute");
691  for (auto task : msg->tasks) {
692  // pub task_result when finshed task or failed task
693  if (task.task.task_name.compare("CALL") == 0) {
694  update_task_status_in_monitoring_data(msg->header, task);
695  }
696  if (task.task.task_name.compare("TRANSFER") == 0) {
697  update_task_status_in_monitoring_data(msg->header, task);
698  }
699  if (task.task.task_name.compare("BACK_TO_BASE") == 0) {
700  update_task_status_in_monitoring_data(msg->header, task);
701  }
702  if (task.task.task_name.compare("SERVING") == 0) {
703  update_task_status_in_monitoring_data(msg->header, task);
704  }
705  if (task.task.task_name.compare("GO_INTO_EV") == 0) {
706  update_task_status_in_monitoring_data(msg->header, task);
707  }
708  if (task.task.task_name.compare("GO_OUT_OF_EV") == 0) {
709  update_task_status_in_monitoring_data(msg->header, task);
710  }
711  if (task.task.task_name.compare("TRANSFER_INPUT") == 0) {
712  update_task_status_in_monitoring_data(msg->header, task);
713  }
714  if (task.task.task_name.compare("SERVE_CUSTOMER") == 0) {
715  update_task_status_in_monitoring_data(msg->header, task);
716  }
717  if (task.task.task_name.compare("KNOCK") == 0) {
718  update_task_status_in_monitoring_data(msg->header, task);
719  }
720  if (task.task.task_name.compare("TRANSFER_FAILED") == 0) {
721  update_task_status_in_monitoring_data(msg->header, task);
722  }
723  if (task.task.task_name.compare("TRANSFER_CANCELED") == 0) {
724  update_task_status_in_monitoring_data(msg->header, task);
725  }
726  if (task.task.task_name.compare("DOCENT") == 0) {
727  update_task_status_in_monitoring_data(msg->header, task);
728  }
729  if (task.task.task_name.compare("PATROL") == 0) {
730  update_task_status_in_monitoring_data(msg->header, task);
731  }
732  if (task.task.task_name.compare("DELIVERY_ITEMS") == 0) {
733  update_task_status_in_monitoring_data(msg->header, task);
734  }
735  if (task.task.task_name.compare("HELLO_CUSTOMER") == 0) {
736  update_task_status_in_monitoring_data(msg->header, task);
737  }
738  }
739  }, sub_opt_robot_cbgroup);
740 }

742 void EveRobotAgent::init_ros_subscriber_hw()
743 {
744  auto sub_opt_gaemi_server_cbgroup = rclcpp::SubscriptionOptions();
745  sub_opt_gaemi_server_cbgroup.callback_group = callback_group_gaemi_server_;
746 
747  auto sub_opt_robot_cbgroup = rclcpp::SubscriptionOptions();
748  sub_opt_robot_cbgroup.callback_group = callback_group_robot_;
749 
750  motor_state_sub_ = create_subscription<aimbot_hw_interfaces::msg::MotorState>(
751  "/aimbot_base/motor_state", rclcpp::SystemDefaultsQoS(),
752  [this](const aimbot_hw_interfaces::msg::MotorState::SharedPtr msg) -> void {
753  std::lock_guard<std::mutex> lock(mutex_);
754  if (msg->state == aimbot_hw_interfaces::msg::MotorState::BRAKE) {
755  if (last_motor_brake_ != true) {
756  last_motor_brake_ = true;
757  update_safety_state();
758  }
759  } else {
760  last_motor_brake_ = false;
761  update_safety_state();
762  }
763  }, sub_opt_robot_cbgroup);
764 
765  // Manipulator Joint State
766  manipulator_joint_state_sub_ = create_subscription<sensor_msgs::msg::JointState>(
767  "/gc_manipulator/joint_states", rclcpp::SensorDataQoS(),
768  [this](const sensor_msgs::msg::JointState::SharedPtr msg) -> void
769  {
770  std::lock_guard<std::mutex> lock(mutex_);
771  monitoring_data_.manipulator_joint_name = msg->name;
772  monitoring_data_.manipulator_joint_position = msg->position;
773  }, sub_opt_robot_cbgroup);
774 
775  // Motion State
776  motion_state_sub_ = create_subscription<aimbot_state_interfaces::msg::MotionState>(
777  "/motion_state", rclcpp::SystemDefaultsQoS(),
778  [this](const aimbot_state_interfaces::msg::MotionState::SharedPtr msg) -> void
779  {
780  std::lock_guard<std::mutex> lock(mutex_);
781  this->monitoring_data_.position_type = "SLAM";
782  this->monitoring_data_.area_id = msg->floor;
783  this->monitoring_data_.sector = msg->sector;
784  this->monitoring_data_.pose_from_map_current.x = floor(
785  (msg->pose_from_map_current.x) * 100) / 100;
786  this->monitoring_data_.pose_from_map_current.y = floor(
787  (msg->pose_from_map_current.y) * 100) / 100;
788  this->monitoring_data_.pose_from_map_current.theta = msg->pose_from_map_current.theta;
789  this->ev_status_array_.atm_floor = msg->atm_floor;
790  }, sub_opt_robot_cbgroup);
791 
792  // EV Status Array Sub
793  ev_status_array_sub_ = create_subscription<perception_interfaces::msg::EVStatusArray>(
794  "/ev_status_array", rclcpp::SystemDefaultsQoS(),
795  [this](const perception_interfaces::msg::EVStatusArray::SharedPtr msg) -> void
796  {
797  std::lock_guard<std::mutex> lock(mutex_);
798  // RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(get_logger(), "GO_INTO_EV target_name : " << msg->ev_num.size());
799  this->ev_status_array_.ev_num.clear();
800  this->ev_status_array_.ev_status.clear();
801  if (msg->ev_num.size() != 0) {
802  for (size_t i = 0; i < msg->ev_num.size(); ++i) {
803  this->ev_status_array_.ev_num.push_back(msg->ev_num[i]);
804  eve_server_interfaces::msg::EvStatus ev_temp;
805  ev_temp.ev_floor = msg->ev_status[i].ev_floor;
806  ev_temp.current_floor = msg->ev_status[i].current_floor;
807  ev_temp.ev_door_status = msg->ev_status[i].ev_door_status;
808  ev_temp.ev_direction = msg->ev_status[i].ev_direction;
809  ev_temp.in_ev = msg->ev_status[i].in_ev;
810  this->ev_status_array_.ev_status.push_back(ev_temp);
811  }
812  }
813  ev_status_array_pub_->publish(this->ev_status_array_);
814  }, sub_opt_robot_cbgroup);
815 
816 
817  // odom
818  odom_sub_ = create_subscription<nav_msgs::msg::Odometry>(
819  "/odom", rclcpp::SystemDefaultsQoS(),
820  [this](const nav_msgs::msg::Odometry::SharedPtr msg) -> void
821  {
822  std::lock_guard<std::mutex> lock(mutex_);
823  this->monitoring_data_.linear_velocity = floor(msg->twist.twist.linear.x * 100) / 100;
824  this->monitoring_data_.angular_velocity = floor(
825  ((msg->twist.twist.angular.z) * (180.0 / M_PI)) * 100) / 100;
826  }, sub_opt_robot_cbgroup);
827 
828  // cargo
829  cargo_door_state_sub_ = create_subscription<aimbot_hw_interfaces::msg::CargoDoorStatus>(
830  "/aimbot_base/cargo_door_status", rclcpp::SystemDefaultsQoS(),
831  [this](const aimbot_hw_interfaces::msg::CargoDoorStatus::SharedPtr msg) -> void
832  {
833  std::lock_guard<std::mutex> lock(mutex_);
834  this->monitoring_data_.tray_name.clear();
835  this->monitoring_data_.tray_locked.clear();
836  for (size_t index = 0; index < msg->state.size(); index++) {
837  this->monitoring_data_.tray_name.push_back("TRAY" + std::to_string(index + 1));
838  this->monitoring_data_.tray_locked.push_back(
839  msg->state.at(index) == aimbot_hw_interfaces::msg::CargoDoorStatus::CLOSE);
840  }
841  }, sub_opt_robot_cbgroup);
842 
843  // task_sequence
844  compressed_image_sub_ = create_subscription<sensor_msgs::msg::CompressedImage>(
845  "/gc_manipulator/zedm/zed_node/left_raw/image_raw_color/compressed", 0,
846  std::bind(
847  &EveRobotAgent::compressed_image_callback, this,
848  std::placeholders::_1), sub_opt_robot_cbgroup);
849  maintenance_mode_sub_ = create_subscription<std_msgs::msg::Bool>(
850  "/maintenance_mode", rclcpp::SystemDefaultsQoS(),
851  [this](const std_msgs::msg::Bool::SharedPtr msg) -> void
852  {
853  write_maintenance_mode(msg->data);
854  }, sub_opt_robot_cbgroup);
855 
856  detector_status_sub_ = create_subscription<perception_interfaces::msg::DetectorStates>(
857  "perception_manager/detector_states", rclcpp::SystemDefaultsQoS(),
858  [this](const perception_interfaces::msg::DetectorStates::SharedPtr msg) -> void {
859  this->monitoring_data_.detector_name.clear();
860  this->monitoring_data_.detector_state.clear();
861  for (size_t index = 0; index < msg->detector_name.size(); index++) {
862  this->monitoring_data_.detector_name.push_back((msg->detector_name.at(index)));
863  this->monitoring_data_.detector_state.push_back(
864  msg->detector_state.at(index));
865  }
866  }, sub_opt_robot_cbgroup);
867 }

869 void EveRobotAgent::init_sensor_subscriber()
870 {
871  auto sub_opt_gaemi_server_cbgroup = rclcpp::SubscriptionOptions();
872  sub_opt_gaemi_server_cbgroup.callback_group = callback_group_gaemi_server_;
873 
874  auto sub_opt_robot_cbgroup = rclcpp::SubscriptionOptions();
875  sub_opt_robot_cbgroup.callback_group = callback_group_robot_;
876 
877  estop_state_sub_ = create_subscription<std_msgs::msg::Bool>(
878  "/aimbot_base/estop_status", rclcpp::SystemDefaultsQoS(),
879  [this](const std_msgs::msg::Bool::SharedPtr msg) -> void
880  {
881  std::lock_guard<std::mutex> lock(mutex_);
882  this->monitoring_data_.emergency_status = msg->data;
883  }, sub_opt_robot_cbgroup);
884 
885  // Battery
886  battery_state_sub_ = create_subscription<sensor_msgs::msg::BatteryState>(
887  "/aimbot_base/battery_state", rclcpp::SystemDefaultsQoS(),
888  [this](
889  const sensor_msgs::msg::BatteryState::SharedPtr msg) -> void
890  {
891  std::lock_guard<std::mutex> lock(mutex_);
892  switch (msg->power_supply_status) {
893  case sensor_msgs::msg::BatteryState::POWER_SUPPLY_STATUS_CHARGING:
894  battery_status_ = "Charging";
895  this->monitoring_data_.docked_status = true;
896  break;
897  case sensor_msgs::msg::BatteryState::POWER_SUPPLY_STATUS_UNKNOWN:
898  battery_status_ = "Unknown (Docked)";
899  this->monitoring_data_.docked_status = true;
900  break;
901  case sensor_msgs::msg::BatteryState::POWER_SUPPLY_STATUS_NOT_CHARGING:
902  battery_status_ = "Not Charging";
903  this->monitoring_data_.docked_status = false;
904  break;
905  default:
906  battery_status_ = "-";
907  this->monitoring_data_.docked_status = false;
908  break;
909  }
910  this->monitoring_data_.battery_percentage =
911  static_cast<char>(((msg->percentage) * 100) * (10 / 10.0));
912 
913  this->battery_state_data_.power_supply_status = msg->power_supply_status;
914  this->battery_state_data_.voltage = msg->voltage;
915  }, sub_opt_robot_cbgroup);
916 
917  // Lidar
918  lidar_sub_ = create_subscription<sensor_msgs::msg::LaserScan>(
919  "/scan", rclcpp::SensorDataQoS(),
920  [this](const sensor_msgs::msg::LaserScan::SharedPtr msg) -> void
921  {
922  std::lock_guard<std::mutex> lock(mutex_);
923  monitoring_data_.lidar_angle.clear();
924  monitoring_data_.lidar_range.clear();
925  for (float angle = -M_PIf32; angle < M_PIf32; angle += 1.0f * M_PIf32 / 180.0f) {
926  float index = (angle - msg->angle_min) / msg->angle_increment;
927  if (index > 0.0f && index < (msg->ranges).size()) {
928  monitoring_data_.lidar_angle.push_back(angle);
929  monitoring_data_.lidar_range.push_back(msg->ranges.at(static_cast<size_t>(index)));
930  }
931  }
932  }, sub_opt_robot_cbgroup);
933 
934  // safety state
935  tof_safety_state_sub_ = create_subscription<aimbot_hw_interfaces::msg::SafetyFilterState>(
936  "/tof_safety_filter_state", rclcpp::SystemDefaultsQoS(),
937  [this](const aimbot_hw_interfaces::msg::SafetyFilterState::SharedPtr msg) -> void {
938  if (msg->state == aimbot_hw_interfaces::msg::SafetyFilterState::BRAKE) {
939  std::lock_guard<std::mutex> lock(mutex_);
940  if (last_tof_brake_ != true) {
941  last_tof_brake_ = true;
942  update_safety_state();
943  }
944  } else {
945  last_tof_brake_ = false;
946  update_safety_state();
947  }
948  }, sub_opt_robot_cbgroup);
949 }

1347  app_service_srv_ = create_service<eve_server_interfaces::srv::AppService>(
1348  robot_serial + "/external/app_service",
1349  std::bind(
1350  &EveRobotAgent::app_service_srv_callback, this, _1,
1351  _2), rmw_qos_profile_services_default, callback_group_gaemi_server_);
1352 
1353  call_recovery_srv_ = create_service<eve_server_interfaces::srv::RecoveryService>(
1354  robot_serial + "/control/recovery_service",
1355  std::bind(&EveRobotAgent::call_recovery_srv_callback, this, _1, _2),
1356  rmw_qos_profile_services_default, callback_group_gaemi_server_);
1357 
1358  execute_tree_srv_outer_ = create_service<eve_server_interfaces::srv::ExecuteTree>(
1359  robot_serial + "/tree/execute_tree",
1360  std::bind(&EveRobotAgent::execute_tree_srv_callback, this, _1, _2),
1361  rmw_qos_profile_services_default, callback_group_gaemi_server_);
1362 }
1363 
1364 void EveRobotAgent::send_task_command(int command)
1365 {
1366  std_msgs::msg::Int8 command_msg;
1367  switch (command) {
1368  // case TaskCommand::STOP:
1369  // stop_task_pub_->publish(stop_msg);
1370  // return;
1371 
1372  case TaskCommand::START:
1373  case TaskCommand::RESUME:
1374  case TaskCommand::PAUSE:
1375  case TaskCommand::STOP:
1376  case TaskCommand::STOP_ALL:
1377  case TaskCommand::CANCEL:
1378  command_msg.data = command;
1379  task_command_pub_->publish(command_msg);
1380  break;
1381 
1382  default:
1383  break;
1384  }
1385 }
1386 
1387 void EveRobotAgent::execute_tree_srv_callback(
1388  const std::shared_ptr<eve_server_interfaces::srv::ExecuteTree::Request> request,
1389  std::shared_ptr<eve_server_interfaces::srv::ExecuteTree::Response> response)
1390 {
1391  auto req = std::make_shared<task_manager_interfaces::srv::AddTask::Request>();
1392  auto prev_req_task = std::make_shared<task_manager_interfaces::srv::AddTask::Request>();
1393  if (!add_task_cli_inner_->wait_for_service(std::chrono::milliseconds(600))) {
1394  RCLCPP_INFO(this->get_logger(), "[ExecuteTree] No response from server!");
1395  response->result_code = 1000;
1396  response->result = false;
1397  }
1398  if (task_status_data_.tasks.empty() || task_status_data_.tasks[0].task_status != "RUNNING") {
1399  write_pub_agent_log(
1400  "FMS-Execute Tree => Tree Executor Start",
1401  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_LOW,
1402  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::TYPE_INFO);
1403  if (request->task_name == "HELLO_CUSTOMER") {
1404  write_pub_agent_log(
1405  "FMS-Excute Tree => HELLO_CUSTOMER", eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_LOW,
1406  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::TYPE_INFO);
1407  req->index = 1;
1408  req->requested_time = get_clock()->now();
1409  req->task.task_name = request->task_name;
1410  req->task.tree_name = hello_customer_tree_name_;
1411  auto future = add_task_cli_inner_->async_send_request(req);
1412  auto result = future.wait_for(std::chrono::seconds(1));
1413  if (result == std::future_status::ready) {
1414  auto res = future.get();
1415  if (res->result == true) {
1416  write_pub_agent_log(
1417  "FMS-Excute Tree => HELLO_CUSTOMER => ADD TASK SUCCESS",
1418  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_LOW,
1419  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::TYPE_INFO);
1420 // sleep(1);
1421  req->index = 2;
1422  req->requested_time = get_clock()->now();
1423  req->task.task_name = 'PATROL';
1424  req->task.tree_name = patrol_tree_name_;
1425  auto future = add_task_cli_inner_->async_send_request(req);
1426  auto result = future.wait_for(std::chrono::seconds(1));
1427  if (result == std::future_status::ready) {
1428  auto res = future.get();
1429  if (res->result == true) {
1430  write_pub_agent_log(
1431  "FMS-Excute Tree => HELLO_CUSTOMER => ADD TASK PATROL SUCCESS",
1432  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_LOW,
1433  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::TYPE_INFO);
1434  sleep(1);
1435  send_task_command(TaskCommand::START);
1436  response->result = true;
1437  }
1438  } else {
1439  write_pub_agent_log(
1440  "FMS-Excute Tree => HELLO_CUSTOMER => ADD TASK PATROL FAILED",
1441  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_LOW,
1442  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::TYPE_INFO);
1443 // sleep(1);
1444 // send_task_command(TaskCommand::START);
1445  response->result = false;
1446  }
1447 // send_task_command(TaskCommand::START);
1448 // response->result = true;
1449  } else {
1450  write_pub_agent_log(
1451  "FMS-Excute Tree => HELLO_CUSTOMER => ADD TASK Failed",
1452  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_LOW,
1453  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::TYPE_INFO);
1454  response->result = false;
1455  }
1456  } else {
1457  write_pub_agent_log(
1458  "FMS-Excute Tree => HELLO_CUSTOMER => ADD TASK Future timeout!",
1459  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_LOW,
1460  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::TYPE_INFO);
1461  response->result = false;
1462  }
1463  }
1464  if (request->task_name == "GO_INTO_EV") {
1465  write_pub_agent_log(
1466  "FMS-Excute Tree => GO_INTO_EV", eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_LOW,
1467  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::TYPE_INFO);
1468  req->index = 1;
1469  req->requested_time = get_clock()->now();
1470  req->task.task_name = request->task_name;
1471  req->task.tree_name = go_into_ev_tree_name_;
1472  task_manager_interfaces::msg::Blackboard blackboard;
1473  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(
1474  get_logger(),
1475  "tree info size " << request->tree_info.size());
1476  for (auto tree_info : request->tree_info) {
1477  if (tree_info.name.compare("elevator_num") == 0) {
1478  blackboard.blackboard_type = task_manager_interfaces::msg::Blackboard::STRING;
1479  blackboard.blackboard_key = tree_info.name;
1480  blackboard.blackboard_value = tree_info.value;
1481  req->task.blackboard_data.push_back(blackboard);
1482  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(get_logger(), "GO_INTO_EV elevator_num : " << tree_info.value);
1483  }
1484  if (tree_info.name.compare("prev_task_name") == 0) {

1487  prev_req_task->task.task_name = "CALL";

1491  prev_req_task->task.task_name = "TRANSFER";
1492  prev_req_task->task.tree_name = move_to_customer_tree_name_;
1493  } else if (tree_info.value == "BACK_TO_BASE") {
1494  prev_req_task->index = task_manager_interfaces::srv::AddTask::Request::END;
1495  prev_req_task->task.task_name = "BACK_TO_BASE";
1496  prev_req_task->task.tree_name = back_to_base_tree_name_;
1497  }
1498  }
1499  if (tree_info.name.compare("prev_target_poi") == 0) {
1500  blackboard.blackboard_type = task_manager_interfaces::msg::Blackboard::STRING;
1501  blackboard.blackboard_key = tree_info.name;
1502  blackboard.blackboard_value = tree_info.value;
1503  req->task.blackboard_data.push_back(blackboard);

1505  task_manager_interfaces::msg::Blackboard blackboard;
1506  blackboard.blackboard_type = task_manager_interfaces::msg::Blackboard::STRING;

1508  blackboard.blackboard_value = tree_info.value;

1516  blackboard.blackboard_value = tree_info.value;

1531  "blackboard_data parse error! size data: " << req->task.blackboard_data.size());
1532  response->result_code = 1001;
1533  response->result = false;

1536  "FMS-Excute Tree => GO_INTO_EV => parser ok",
1537  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_LOW,

1804  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(get_logger(), "KNOCK knock prev_tray_info : " << tree_info.value);
1805  }
1806  if (tree_info.name.compare("prev_target_poi") == 0) {
1807  blackboard.blackboard_type = task_manager_interfaces::msg::Blackboard::STRING;
1808  blackboard.blackboard_key = "target_name";
1809  blackboard.blackboard_value = tree_info.value;
1810  req->task.blackboard_data.push_back(blackboard);
1811  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(get_logger(), "KNOCK target_name : " << tree_info.value);
1812  }
1813  if (tree_info.name.compare("prev_user_id") == 0) {
1814  blackboard.blackboard_type = task_manager_interfaces::msg::Blackboard::STRING;
1815  blackboard.blackboard_key = tree_info.name;
1816  blackboard.blackboard_value = tree_info.value;
1817  req->task.blackboard_data.push_back(blackboard);
1818  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(get_logger(), "KNOCK user_id : " << tree_info.value);
1819  }
1820  }
1821  if (req->task.blackboard_data.size() != 6) {
1822  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(
1823  get_logger(),
1824  "blackboard_data parse error! size data: " << req->task.blackboard_data.size());
1825  response->result = false;
1826  response->result_code = 1001;
1827  } else {
1828  auto future = add_task_cli_inner_->async_send_request(req);
1829  auto result = future.wait_for(std::chrono::seconds(1));
1830  if (result == std::future_status::ready) {
1831  auto res = future.get();
1832  if (res->result == true) {
1833  write_pub_agent_log(
1834  "FMS=>KNOCK=>ADD_TASK SUCCESS", eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_LOW,
1835  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::TYPE_INFO);
1836  response->result = true;
1837  response->result_code = 0;
1838  if (call_set_task_command_service(
1839  task_manager_interfaces::srv::SetTaskCommand::Request::START, "") == true)
1840  {
1841  write_pub_agent_log(
1842  "FMS=>KNOCK=>ADD_TASK=>START SUCCESS",
1843  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_LOW,
1844  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::TYPE_INFO);
1845  response->result = true;
1846  response->result_code = 0;
1847  } else {
1848  write_pub_agent_log(
1849  "FMS=>KNOCK=>ADD_TASK=>START FAILED", eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_LOW,
1850  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::TYPE_INFO);
1851  response->result = false;
1852  }
1853  } else if (res->result == false) {
1854  write_pub_agent_log(
1855  "FMS=>KNOCK=>ADD_TASK Failed", eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_LOW,
1856  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::TYPE_INFO);
1857  response->result = res->result;
1858  }
1859  } else {
1860  response->result = false;
1861  }
1862  }
1863  }
1864  } else {
1865  write_pub_agent_log(
1866  "FMS-Execute Tree, You need to stop task before", eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_LOW,
1867  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::TYPE_INFO);
1868  response->result = false;
1869  }
1870 }

1888 void EveRobotAgent::update_task_status_in_monitoring_data(
1889  std_msgs::msg::Header header,
1890  task_manager_interfaces::msg::TaskListItem task)
1891 {
1892  std::string status;
1893  if (task.status == task_manager_interfaces::msg::TaskListItem::FINISHED ||
1894  task.status == task_manager_interfaces::msg::TaskListItem::FAILED)
1895  {
1896  pub_task_result_data(header.stamp, task);
1897  return;
1898  } else if (task.status == task_manager_interfaces::msg::TaskListItem::IDLE) {
1899  status = "WAITING";
1900  } else if (task.status == task_manager_interfaces::msg::TaskListItem::RUNNING) {
1901  status = "RUNNING";
1902  }
1903 
1904  if (task.user_id == "") {
1905  task_data_.task_id = task.id;
1906  task_data_.caller_id = "";
1907  } else {
1908  task_data_.task_id = task.id;
1909  task_data_.caller_id = task.user_id;
1910  }
1911  task_data_.task_type = task.task.task_name;
1912  try {
1913  task_data_.target_poi = task.target_poi;
1914  } catch (std::out_of_range & e) {
1915  task_data_.target_poi = "Unknown";
1916  }
1917  {
1918  char log_time[30];
1919  std::time_t raw_time = static_cast<std::time_t>(task.start_time.sec);
1920  struct tm timeinfo;
1921  localtime_r(&raw_time, &timeinfo);
1922  std::strftime(log_time, sizeof(log_time), "%Y%m%d%H%M%S", &timeinfo);
1923  task_data_.start_date = log_time;
1924  }
1925  {
1926  char log_time[30];
1927  std::time_t raw_time = static_cast<std::time_t>(task.start_time.sec);
1928  struct tm timeinfo;
1929  localtime_r(&raw_time, &timeinfo);
1930  timeinfo.tm_min += task.estimated_remaining_time;
1931  std::strftime(log_time, sizeof(log_time), "%Y%m%d%H%M%S", &timeinfo);
1932  task_data_.est_end_date = log_time;
1933  }
1934  task_data_.reg_time = convert_ros_time_to_utc(task.requested_time);
1935  task_data_.task_status = status;
1936  task_status_data_.tasks.push_back(task_data_);
1937  monitoring_data_.tasks.push_back(task_data_);
1938 }

1941 void EveRobotAgent::publish_server_noti(robotis_server_interfaces::msg::FmsNotify msg)
1942 {
1943  std::lock_guard<std::mutex> lock(mutex_);
1944  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Notify server_noti;
1945  server_noti.header = msg.header;
1946  server_noti.level = msg.level;
1947  server_noti.source = msg.source;
1948  // needs to APP notify publish
1949  server_noti.keyword = msg.keyword;
1950  for (size_t i = 0; i < msg.additional_infos.size(); i++) {
1951  server_noti.additional_infos.push_back(msg.additional_infos.at(i));
1952  }
1953  server_noti.robot_serial = robot_serial_;
1954  server_noti.site_id = service_site_;
1955  server_noti_pub_->publish(server_noti);
1956 }

1958 void EveRobotAgent::app_service_srv_callback(
1959  const std::shared_ptr<eve_server_interfaces::srv::AppService::Request> request,
1960  std::shared_ptr<eve_server_interfaces::srv::AppService::Response> response)
1961 {
1962  if (request->service_name == "REINPUT") {
1963  auto result = app_service_reinput();
1964  response->result = result;
1965  } else if (request->service_name == "APP_STOP") {
1966  publish_prev_cargo_data();
1967  if (call_set_task_command_service(
1968  task_manager_interfaces::srv::SetTaskCommand::Request::STOP, "") == true)
1969  {
1970  response->result = true;
1971  } else {
1972  response->result = false;
1973  }
1974  // TEST
1975  } else if (request->service_name == "CANCEL_TRANSFER") {
1976  auto result = app_service_cancel_transfer();
1977  response->result = result;
1978  } else if (request->service_name == "UI_CONTROL") {
1979  set_gui_info_data_.data = request->value;
1980  set_gui_info_data_pub_->publish(set_gui_info_data_);
1981  write_pub_agent_log(
1982  "APP => ui_control ",
1983  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_LOW,
1984  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::TYPE_INFO);
1985  response->result = true;
1986  } else if (request->service_name == "USER_COMMAND") {
1987  auto user_id = request->user_id;
1988  auto command = request->usr_command;
1989  auto result = call_set_user_command(user_id, command);
1990  if (result == true) {
1991  write_pub_agent_log(
1992  "APP => SET_USER_COMMAND SUCCESS",
1993  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_LOW,
1994  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::TYPE_INFO);
1995  response->result = true;
1996  } else {
1997  write_pub_agent_log(
1998  "APP => SET_USER_COMMAND Failed",
1999  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_LOW,
2000  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::TYPE_INFO);
2001  response->result = false;
2002  }
2003  } else if (request->service_name == "USER_CANCEL") {
2004  auto user_id = request->user_id;
2005  auto command = eve_server_interfaces::srv::AppService::Request::CANCEL;
2006  auto result = call_set_user_command(user_id, command);
2007  if (result == true) {
2008  write_pub_agent_log(
2009  "APP => USER_CANCEL SUCCESS",
2010  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_LOW,
2011  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::TYPE_INFO);
2012  response->result = true;
2013  } else {
2014  write_pub_agent_log(
2015  "APP => USER_CANCEL Failed",
2016  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_LOW,
2017  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::TYPE_INFO);
2018  response->result = false;
2019  }
2020  } else if (request->service_name == "BACK_TO_BASE") {
2021  auto result = app_service_back_to_base();
2022  response->result = result;
2023  } else if (request->service_name == "DOCENT") {
2024  auto result = app_service_docent(request->value);
2025  if (result == true) {
2026  write_pub_agent_log(
2027  "APP => DOCENT REQUEST SUCCESS",
2028  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_LOW,
2029  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::TYPE_INFO);
2030  response->result = true;
2031  } else {
2032  write_pub_agent_log(
2033  "APP => DOCENT REQUEST Failed",
2034  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_LOW,
2035  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::TYPE_INFO);
2036  response->result = false;
2037  }
2038  } else if (request->service_name == "DELIVERY_ITEMS") {
2039  auto result = app_service_delivery_items(request->user_id, request->value);
2040  if (result == true) {
2041  write_pub_agent_log(
2042  "APP => DELIVERY_ITMES REQUEST SUCCESS",
2043  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_LOW,
2044  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::TYPE_INFO);
2045  response->result = true;
2046  } else {
2047  write_pub_agent_log(
2048  "APP => DELIVERY_ITMES REQUEST Failed",
2049  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_LOW,
2050  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::TYPE_INFO);
2051  response->result = false;
2052  }
2053  } else if (request->service_name == "PATROL") {
2054  write_pub_agent_log(
2055  "미구현 기능입니다",
2056  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_LOW,
2057  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::TYPE_INFO);
2058  response->result = false;
2059  } else {
2060  write_pub_agent_log(
2061  "APP => Service => UNKOWN FAILED, NOT SUPPORT SERVICE ",
2062  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_LOW,
2063  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::TYPE_INFO);
2064  response->result = false;
2065  }
2066 }

2106 bool EveRobotAgent::app_service_reinput()
2107 {
2108  write_pub_agent_log(
2109  "APP => REINPUT", eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_LOW,
2110  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::TYPE_INFO);
2111  auto result = call_set_task_command_service(
2112  task_manager_interfaces::srv::SetTaskCommand::Request::STOP_ALL, "");
2113  if (result == true) {
2114  write_pub_agent_log(
2115  "APP => REINPUT => STOP_ALL SUCCESS", eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_LOW,
2116  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::TYPE_INFO);
2117  auto req = std::make_shared<task_manager_interfaces::srv::AddTask::Request>();
2118  if (!add_task_cli_inner_->wait_for_service(std::chrono::milliseconds(200))) {
2119  write_pub_agent_log(
2120  "APP => REINPUT => ADD_TASK SERVER NOT FOUND!",
2121  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_LOW,
2122  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::TYPE_INFO);
2123  return false;
2124  }
2125  req->index = task_manager_interfaces::srv::AddTask::Request::FRONT;
2126  req->task.task_name = 'TRANSFER_INPUT';
2127  req->task.tree_name = transfer_input_tree_name_;
2128  auto future = add_task_cli_inner_->async_send_request(req);
2129  auto result = future.wait_for(std::chrono::seconds(1));
2130  if (result == std::future_status::ready) {
2131  auto result = call_set_task_command_service(
2132  task_manager_interfaces::srv::SetTaskCommand::Request::START, "");
2133  if (result == true) {
2134  write_pub_agent_log(
2135  "APP => REINPUT => ADD_TASK SUCCESS => START SUCCESS",
2136  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_LOW,
2137  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::TYPE_INFO);
2138  auto result = call_set_gui_page("InputDelivery", "");
2139  if (result == true) {
2140  return true;
2141  } else {
2142  return false;
2143  }
2144  } else {
2145  write_pub_agent_log(
2146  "APP => REINPUT => ADD_TASK SUCCESS => START FAILED",
2147  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_LOW,
2148  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::TYPE_INFO);
2149  return false;
2150  }
2151  } else {
2152  return false;
2153  }
2154  } else {
2155  return false;
2156  }
2157 }

2163  if (!add_task_cli_inner_->wait_for_service(std::chrono::milliseconds(200))) {
2164  RCLCPP_INFO(this->get_logger(), "[AddTask] failed to add task");
2165  return false;
2166  }
2167  req->index = task_manager_interfaces::srv::AddTask::Request::END;
2168  req->requested_time = get_clock()->now();
2169  if (user_id != "") {
2170  req->user_id = user_id;
2171  }

2176  blackboard.blackboard_key = "target_name";
2177  blackboard.blackboard_value = target_poi;
2178  req->task.blackboard_data.push_back(blackboard);

2180  blackboard.blackboard_key = "free_mode";
2181  blackboard.blackboard_value = "Y";
2182  req->task.blackboard_data.push_back(blackboard);
2183  req->task.tree_name_on_failure = back_to_customer_tree_name_;
2184  req->task.tree_name_on_cancel = back_to_customer_tree_name_;
2185  auto future = add_task_cli_inner_->async_send_request(req);
2186  auto result = future.wait_for(std::chrono::seconds(1));
2187  if (result != std::future_status::ready) {
2188  RCLCPP_INFO(this->get_logger(), "[AddTask] failed to add task");
2189  return false;
2190  }
2191  return true;

2304  req->task.blackboard_data.push_back(blackboard);
2305  req->task.tree_name_on_failure = back_to_customer_tree_name_;
2306  req->task.tree_name_on_cancel = back_to_customer_tree_name_;
2307  auto future = add_task_cli_inner_->async_send_request(req);
2308  auto result = future.wait_for(std::chrono::seconds(1));
2309  if (result != std::future_status::ready) {
2310  RCLCPP_INFO(this->get_logger(), "[AddTask] failed to add task");
2311  return false;
2312  }
2313  // 정지 상태여서 시작 안될 경우를 대비한 START
2314  auto start_result = call_set_task_command_service(
2315  task_manager_interfaces::srv::SetTaskCommand::Request::START, "");
2316  if (start_result == true) {
2317  return true;
2318  } else {
2319  return false;
2320  }
2321  }
2322 }

2368 void EveRobotAgent::publish_prev_cargo_data()
2369 {
2370  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Notify noti;
2371  eve_server_interfaces::msg::AdditionalField add_field;
2372  for (auto tasks : task_list_.tasks) {
2373  for (auto blackboard : tasks.task.blackboard_data) {
2374  if (blackboard.blackboard_key == "target_name") {
2375  add_field.name = "cargoGoal";
2376  add_field.value = blackboard.blackboard_value;
2377  noti.additional_infos.push_back(add_field);
2378  }
2379  if (blackboard.blackboard_key == "tray_num") {
2380  add_field.name = "cargoNum";
2381  add_field.value = blackboard.blackboard_value;
2382  noti.additional_infos.push_back(add_field);
2383  }
2384  }
2385  }
2386  noti.robot_serial = robot_serial_;
2387  noti.site_id = service_site_;
2388  noti.level = eve_server_interfaces::msg::Notify::INFO;
2389  noti.keyword = "APP_STOP";
2390  noti.header.stamp = this->now();
2391  noti.source = "EveRobotAgent";
2392  server_noti_pub_->publish(noti);

2670 void EveRobotAgent::change_map_service_outer_callback(
2671  const std::shared_ptr<eve_server_interfaces::srv::ChangeMap::Request> request,
2672  std::shared_ptr<eve_server_interfaces::srv::ChangeMap::Response> response)
2673 {
2674  std::lock_guard<std::mutex> lock(service_mutex_);
2675  if (!change_map_service_inner_cli->wait_for_service(std::chrono::milliseconds(200))) {
2676  RCLCPP_ERROR_STREAM(
2677  get_logger(),
2678  "Failed to connect change_map_service_inner_cli [change_map_service_inner_cli]");
2679  response->result = eve_server_interfaces::srv::ChangeMap::Response::RESULT_LOAD_MAP_FAILURE;
2680  }
2681  auto req = std::make_shared<aimbot_state_interfaces::srv::ChangeMap::Request>();
2682  req->map_name = request->map_name;
2683  auto future = change_map_service_inner_cli->async_send_request(req);
2684  auto result = future.wait_for(std::chrono::seconds(1));
2685  if (result == std::future_status::ready) {
2686  auto res = future.get();
2687  if (res->result == aimbot_state_interfaces::srv::ChangeMap::Response::RESULT_SUCCESS) {
2688  response->result = eve_server_interfaces::srv::ChangeMap::Response::RESULT_SUCCESS;
2689  } else {
2690  switch (res->result) {
2691  case aimbot_state_interfaces::srv::ChangeMap::Response::RESULT_MAP_DOES_NOT_EXIST:
2692  response->result =
2693  eve_server_interfaces::srv::ChangeMap::Response::RESULT_MAP_DOES_NOT_EXIST;
2694  break;
2695  case aimbot_state_interfaces::srv::ChangeMap::Response::RESULT_INVALID_MAP_DATA:
2696  response->result =
2697  eve_server_interfaces::srv::ChangeMap::Response::RESULT_INVALID_MAP_DATA;
2698  break;
2699  case aimbot_state_interfaces::srv::ChangeMap::Response::RESULT_INVALID_MAP_METADATA:
2700  response->result =
2701  eve_server_interfaces::srv::ChangeMap::Response::RESULT_INVALID_MAP_METADATA;
2702  break;
2703  case aimbot_state_interfaces::srv::ChangeMap::Response::RESULT_SERVICE_LOAD_FAILURE:
2704  response->result =
2705  eve_server_interfaces::srv::ChangeMap::Response::RESULT_SERVICE_LOAD_FAILURE;
2706  break;
2707  case aimbot_state_interfaces::srv::ChangeMap::Response::RESULT_SERVICE_CALL_TIMEOUT:
2708  response->result =
2709  eve_server_interfaces::srv::ChangeMap::Response::RESULT_SERVICE_CALL_TIMEOUT;
2710  break;
2711  case aimbot_state_interfaces::srv::ChangeMap::Response::RESULT_SERVICE_CALL_FAILURE:
2712  response->result =
2713  eve_server_interfaces::srv::ChangeMap::Response::RESULT_SERVICE_CALL_FAILURE;
2714  break;
2715  case aimbot_state_interfaces::srv::ChangeMap::Response::RESULT_LOAD_MAP_FAILURE:
2716  response->result =
2717  eve_server_interfaces::srv::ChangeMap::Response::RESULT_LOAD_MAP_FAILURE;
2718  break;
2719  }
2720  }
2721  } else {
2722  response->result = eve_server_interfaces::srv::ChangeMap::Response::RESULT_UNDEFINED_FAILURE;
2723  }
2724 }

3050 bool EveRobotAgent::call_add_task(
3051  std::string user_id, std::string task_type,
3052  std::string destination, std::string requested_time, std::string tray_num, int8_t index)
3053 {
3054  auto req = std::make_shared<task_manager_interfaces::srv::AddTask::Request>();
3055  if (!add_task_cli_inner_->wait_for_service(std::chrono::milliseconds(200))) {
3056  RCLCPP_INFO(this->get_logger(), "[AddTask] failed to add task");
3057  return false;
3058  }
3059  if (task_type == "CALL") {
3060  req->index = index;
3061  req->requested_time = get_clock()->now();
3062  if (user_id != "") {
3063  req->user_id = user_id;
3064  }
3065  req->task.task_name = task_type;
3066  req->task.tree_name = move_goal_tree_name_;
3067  task_manager_interfaces::msg::Blackboard blackboard;
3068  blackboard.blackboard_type = task_manager_interfaces::msg::Blackboard::STRING;
3069  blackboard.blackboard_key = "target_name";
3070  blackboard.blackboard_value = destination;
3071  req->task.blackboard_data.push_back(blackboard);
3072  req->task.tree_name_on_failure = back_to_base_tree_name_;
3073  req->task.tree_name_on_cancel = back_to_base_tree_name_;
3074  auto future = add_task_cli_inner_->async_send_request(req);
3075  auto result = future.wait_for(std::chrono::seconds(1));
3076  if (result != std::future_status::ready) {
3077  RCLCPP_INFO(this->get_logger(), "[AddTask] failed to add task");
3078  return false;
3079  }
3080  return true;
3081  } else if (task_type == "BACK_TO_BASE") {
3082  if (user_id != "") {
3083  req->user_id = user_id;
3084  }
3085  req->index = index;
3086  req->requested_time = get_clock()->now();
3087  req->task.task_name = task_type;
3088  req->task.tree_name = back_to_base_tree_name_;
3089  task_manager_interfaces::msg::Blackboard blackboard;
3090  blackboard.blackboard_type = task_manager_interfaces::msg::Blackboard::STRING;
3091  blackboard.blackboard_key = "target_name";
3092  blackboard.blackboard_value = "service_base";
3093  req->task.blackboard_data.push_back(blackboard);
3094  auto future = add_task_cli_inner_->async_send_request(req);
3095  auto result = future.wait_for(std::chrono::seconds(1));
3096  if (result != std::future_status::ready) {
3097  RCLCPP_INFO(this->get_logger(), "[AddTask] failed to add task");
3098  return false;
3099  }
3100  return true;
3101  } else if (task_type == "TRANSFER") {
3102  if (user_id != "") {
3103  req->user_id = user_id;
3104  }
3105  req->index = index;
3106  req->requested_time = get_clock()->now();
3107  req->task.task_name = task_type;
3108  req->task.tree_name = move_to_customer_tree_name_;
3109  task_manager_interfaces::msg::Blackboard blackboard;
3110  blackboard.blackboard_type = task_manager_interfaces::msg::Blackboard::STRING;
3111  blackboard.blackboard_key = "target_name";
3112  blackboard.blackboard_value = destination;
3113  req->task.blackboard_data.push_back(blackboard);
3114  blackboard.blackboard_type = task_manager_interfaces::msg::Blackboard::STRING;
3115  blackboard.blackboard_key = "start_name";
3116  blackboard.blackboard_value = "service_base";
3117  req->task.blackboard_data.push_back(blackboard);
3118  blackboard.blackboard_type = task_manager_interfaces::msg::Blackboard::INT;
3119  blackboard.blackboard_key = "tray_num";
3120  blackboard.blackboard_value = tray_num;
3121  req->task.blackboard_data.push_back(blackboard);
3122  req->task.tree_name_on_failure = back_to_customer_tree_name_;
3123  req->task.tree_name_on_cancel = back_to_customer_tree_name_;
3124  auto future = add_task_cli_inner_->async_send_request(req);
3125  auto result = future.wait_for(std::chrono::seconds(1));
3126  if (result != std::future_status::ready) {
3127  RCLCPP_INFO(this->get_logger(), "[AddTask] failed to add task");
3128  return false;
3129  }
3130  return true;
3131  } else {
3132  return false;
3133  }

3141  std::lock_guard<std::mutex> lock(service_mutex_);

3143 // write_pub_agent_log(

3174 void EveRobotAgent::calc_button_pose_srv_callback(
3175  const std::shared_ptr<eve_server_interfaces::srv::CalculateButtonPose::Request> request,
3176  std::shared_ptr<eve_server_interfaces::srv::CalculateButtonPose::Response> response)
3177 {
3178  std::lock_guard<std::mutex> lock(service_mutex_);
3179  using PoseEstResult = perception_interfaces::srv::PoseEstimation::Response;
3180  write_pub_agent_log(
3181  "바운딩박스로부터 버튼위치 계산 요청", eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_LOW,
3182  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::TYPE_INFO);
3183 
3185  // call pose_estimation
3186  auto pose_estimation_request_ptr =
3187  std::make_shared<perception_interfaces::srv::PoseEstimation::Request>();
3188  pose_estimation_request_ptr->left_camera.left_top_x = request->left_camera_left_top_x;
3189  pose_estimation_request_ptr->left_camera.left_top_y = request->left_camera_left_top_y;
3190  pose_estimation_request_ptr->left_camera.right_bottom_x = request->left_camera_right_bottom_x;
3191  pose_estimation_request_ptr->left_camera.right_bottom_y = request->left_camera_right_bottom_y;
3192  pose_estimation_request_ptr->right_camera.left_top_x = request->right_camera_left_top_x;
3193  pose_estimation_request_ptr->right_camera.left_top_y = request->right_camera_left_top_y;
3194  pose_estimation_request_ptr->right_camera.right_bottom_x = request->right_camera_right_bottom_x;
3195  pose_estimation_request_ptr->right_camera.right_bottom_y = request->right_camera_right_bottom_y;
3196  auto pose_estimation_future =
3197  pose_estimation_inner_cli_->async_send_request(pose_estimation_request_ptr);
3198 
3199  // get nearest button
3200  auto get_nearest_button_request_ptr =
3201  std::make_shared<aimbot_state_interfaces::srv::GetNearestButton::Request>();
3202  get_nearest_button_request_ptr->reference_frame_id = "zedm_left_camera_frame";
3203  auto get_nearest_button_future =
3204  get_nearest_button_inner_cli_->async_send_request(get_nearest_button_request_ptr);
3205 
3207  // Get response
3208  response->result = eve_server_interfaces::srv::CalculateButtonPose::Response::RESULT_SUCCESS;
3209  // Get pose estimation
3210  auto pose_estimation_result = pose_estimation_future.wait_for(std::chrono::seconds(1));
3211  if (pose_estimation_result != std::future_status::ready) {
3212  write_pub_agent_log(
3213  "바운딩박스 버튼위치 계산 Timeout 실패", eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_LOW,
3214  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::TYPE_ERROR);
3215  response->result =
3216  eve_server_interfaces::srv::CalculateButtonPose::Response::
3217  RESULT_FAILURE_POSE_ESTIMATION_TIMEOUT;
3218  return;
3219  }
3220  auto pose_esti_response = pose_estimation_future.get();
3221  if (pose_esti_response->result !=
3222  PoseEstResult::RESULT_SUCCESS)
3223  {
3224  if (pose_esti_response->result == PoseEstResult::RESULT_INVALID_VALUE) {
3225  write_pub_agent_log(
3226  "유효하지 않은 바운딩박스 값", eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_LOW,
3227  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::TYPE_ERROR);
3228  response->result =
3229  eve_server_interfaces::srv::CalculateButtonPose::Response::RESULT_INVALID_VALUE_FAILURE;
3230  return;
3231  } else if (pose_esti_response->result == PoseEstResult::RESULT_UNDEFINED_FAILURE) {
3232  write_pub_agent_log(
3233  "정의되지 않은 실패", eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_LOW,
3234  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::TYPE_ERROR);
3235  response->result =
3236  eve_server_interfaces::srv::CalculateButtonPose::Response::RESULT_UNDEFINED_FAILURE;
3237  return;
3238  } else {
3239  write_pub_agent_log(
3240  "정의되지 않은 실패", eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_LOW,
3241  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::TYPE_ERROR);
3242  response->result =
3243  eve_server_interfaces::srv::CalculateButtonPose::Response::RESULT_UNDEFINED_FAILURE;
3244  return;
3245  }
3246  }
3247 
3248  // get nearest button
3249  auto get_nearest_button_result = get_nearest_button_future.wait_for(std::chrono::seconds(1));
3250  if (get_nearest_button_result != std::future_status::ready) {
3251  write_pub_agent_log(
3252  "가까운 버튼 받아오기 Timeout 실패", eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_LOW,
3253  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::TYPE_ERROR);
3254  response->result =
3255  eve_server_interfaces::srv::CalculateButtonPose::Response::
3256  RESULT_FAILURE_GET_NEAREST_BUTTON_TIMEOUT;
3257  return;
3258  }
3259  auto get_nearest_button_response = get_nearest_button_future.get();
3260  if (!get_nearest_button_response->success) {
3261  write_pub_agent_log(
3262  "가까운 버튼 받아오기 실패", eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_LOW,
3263  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::TYPE_ERROR);
3264  response->result =
3265  eve_server_interfaces::srv::CalculateButtonPose::Response::
3266  RESULT_FAILURE_NO_REGISTERED_BUTTON;
3267  return;
3268  }
3269 
3271  if (response->result ==
3272  eve_server_interfaces::srv::CalculateButtonPose::Response::RESULT_SUCCESS)
3273  {
3274  geometry_msgs::msg::PoseStamped pose_from_zedm;
3275  if (pose_esti_response->pose.header.frame_id ==
3276  get_nearest_button_response->pose.header.frame_id)
3277  {
3278  pose_from_zedm.header.stamp = pose_esti_response->pose.header.stamp;
3279  pose_from_zedm.header.frame_id = pose_esti_response->pose.header.frame_id;
3280  pose_from_zedm.pose.position = pose_esti_response->pose.pose.position;
3281  pose_from_zedm.pose.orientation = get_nearest_button_response->pose.pose.orientation;
3282  transform_pose(pose_from_zedm, "base_footprint", &response->pose);
3283  } else {
3284  response->result =
3285  eve_server_interfaces::srv::CalculateButtonPose::Response::
3286  RESULT_FAILURE_FRAME_ID_NOT_MATCHED;
3287  return;
3288  }
3289  }

3341 void EveRobotAgent::init_pose_srv_callback(
3342  const std::shared_ptr<eve_server_interfaces::srv::InitPose::Request> request,
3343  std::shared_ptr<eve_server_interfaces::srv::InitPose::Response> response)
3344 {
3345  std::lock_guard<std::mutex> lock(service_mutex_);
3346  if (is_control_ != MONITORING) {
3347  response->result = false;
3348  response->message = "Check Permission";
3349  } else {
3350  try {
3351  auto init_pose = request->init_pose;
3352  geometry_msgs::msg::PoseWithCovarianceStamped init_msg;
3353  init_msg.header.frame_id = "map_current";
3354  init_msg.header.stamp = now();
3355  init_msg.pose.pose.position.x = init_pose.x;
3356  init_msg.pose.pose.position.y = init_pose.y;
3357 
3358  tf2::Quaternion quat;
3359  quat.setRPY(0.0, 0.0, init_pose.theta);
3360  tf2::convert(quat, init_msg.pose.pose.orientation);
3361  init_msg.pose.covariance.at(0) = 0.5 * 0.5;
3362  init_msg.pose.covariance.at(7) = 0.5 * 0.5;
3363  init_msg.pose.covariance.at(35) = (M_PI / 12.0) * (M_PI / 12.0);
3364  init_pose_pub_->publish(init_msg);
3365  response->result = true;
3366  } catch (std::exception & e) {
3367  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(
3368  this->get_logger(),
3369  "[init_pose] Exception: " <<
3370  e.what());
3371  response->result = false;
3372  }
3373  }
3374 }

3421  ")");

3424  "[nav_to_pose_compute_path] tf_q_temp_ !! (q_temp: " << tf_q_temp_ <<
3425  ")");

3435  compute_goal_opitons.result_callback = std::bind(

3437  this, _1);

3447  ")");

3450  rclcpp_action::Client<nav2_msgs::action::NavigateToPose>::SendGoalOptions();

3467  }

3516 void EveRobotAgent::cargo_control_by_user_callback(

3529  cargo_lock_pub_->publish(cargo_control_data_);
3530  response->result = true;
3531  } else {
3532  response->result = false;
3533  }

3535  cargo_control_data_.cargo_num.push_back(1);
3536  if (request->command == "OPEN") {
3537  cargo_unlock_pub_->publish(cargo_control_data_);
3538  response->result = true;
3539  } else if (request->command == "CLOSE") {
3540  cargo_lock_pub_->publish(cargo_control_data_);
3541  response->result = true;
3542  } else {
3543  response->result = false;
3544  }
3545  } else if (request->cargo_num == 2) { // Lower
3546  cargo_control_data_.cargo_num.push_back(2);
3547  if (request->command == "OPEN") {
3548  cargo_unlock_pub_->publish(cargo_control_data_);
3549  response->result = true;
3550  } else if (request->command == "CLOSE") {
3551  cargo_lock_pub_->publish(cargo_control_data_);
3552  response->result = true;
3553  } else {
3554  response->result = false;
3555  }
3556  } else {
3557  response->result = false;
3558  }

3561 void EveRobotAgent::traffic_wait_srv_callback(
3562  const std::shared_ptr<eve_server_interfaces::srv::TrafficWait::Request> request,
3563  std::shared_ptr<eve_server_interfaces::srv::TrafficWait::Response> response)
3564 {
3565  std::lock_guard<std::mutex> lock(service_mutex_);
3566  response->correlation_id = request->correlation_id;
3567  // 타겟 로봇이 지정되지 않고 서비스가 호출되거나,
3568  // 로봇이 대기상태 혹은 에러 상태, 이미 트래픽 컨트롤 명령을 받은 경우
3569  // 마지막 작업 (물건 수령 대기 중인 경우) 에는 서비스 Fail 처리 함
3570  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(
3571  this->get_logger(),
3572  "[traffic_wait_srv_callback] target " << request->target_robot <<
3573  ")");
3574  if (request->target_robot == "" ||
3575  monitoring_data_.robot_status ==
3576  eve_server_interfaces::msg::MonitoringData::ROBOT_STATUS_READY ||
3577  monitoring_data_.emergency_status == true ||
3578  monitoring_data_.robot_status ==
3579  eve_server_interfaces::msg::MonitoringData::ROBOT_STATUS_ERROR ||
3580  monitoring_data_.traffic_wait == true ||
3581  monitoring_data_.present_task_sequence ==
3582  eve_server_interfaces::msg::MonitoringData::LAST_ACTION)
3583  {
3584  response->status = 1111;
3585  response->message = "Not avaliable to traffic control!";
3586  response->result = false;
3587  } else {
3588  // 만약 해당 조건이 아닐 경우, STOP 명령을 날리고
3589  // 로봇의 상태를 변경함.
3590  if (call_set_task_command_service(
3591  task_manager_interfaces::srv::SetTaskCommand::Request::STOP,
3592  request->target_robot) == true)
3593  {
3594  response->status = 0;
3595  response->message = "Traffic controlling....!";
3596  response->result = true;
3597  monitoring_data_.target_robot = request->target_robot;
3598  monitoring_data_.traffic_wait = true;
3599  traffic_control_tick_time_ = now();
3600  is_traffic_control_ = true;
3601  call_set_gui_page("Info", "Traffic Controlling...");
3602  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(
3603  this->get_logger(), "[traffic wait srv success, because of call set_tak_command success");
3604  } else {
3605  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(
3606  this->get_logger(), "[traffic wait srv failed, because of call set_tak_command fail");
3607  response->status = 1111;
3608  response->message = "Failed to traffic controll....!";
3609  response->result = false;
3610  }
3611  }
3612 }

3694 bool EveRobotAgent::call_get_traffic_status()
3695 {
3696 // std::lock_guard<std::mutex> lock(mutex_);
3697  if (!get_traffic_status_cli_outer->wait_for_service(std::chrono::milliseconds(200))) {
3698  RCLCPP_ERROR_STREAM(
3699  get_logger(), "Failed to connect get_traffic_status_srv [get_traffic_status_srv]");
3700  auto req = std::make_shared<eve_server_interfaces::srv::GetTrafficStatus::Request>();
3701  req->target_robot = monitoring_data_.target_robot;
3702  req->robot_serial = robot_serial_;
3703  req->pose_from_map_current.x = monitoring_data_.pose_from_map_current.x;
3704  req->pose_from_map_current.y = monitoring_data_.pose_from_map_current.y;
3705  auto inner_client_callback = [&,
3706  this](rclcpp::Client<eve_server_interfaces::srv::GetTrafficStatus>::SharedFuture
3707  inner_future)
3708  {
3709  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(this->get_logger(), "[get_traffic_status] callback executed");
3710  auto result = inner_future.get();
3711  auto is_success = result->result;
3712  if (is_success == true) {
3713  auto release_lock = result->release_lock;
3714  if (release_lock == true) {
3715  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(get_logger(), "Traffic Control End");
3716  return true;
3717  } else {
3718  traffic_control_tick_time_ = now();
3719  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(get_logger(), "Not release now!");
3720  return false;
3721  }
3722  } else {
3723  RCLCPP_ERROR_STREAM(get_logger(), "Failed to Get Traffic status...");
3724  return false;
3725  }
3726  };
3727  auto future = get_traffic_status_cli_outer->async_send_request(req, inner_client_callback);
3728  auto result = future.wait_for(std::chrono::seconds(1));
3729  switch (result) {
3730  case std::future_status::ready:
3731  break;
3732  case std::future_status::timeout:
3733  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(this->get_logger(), "[inner service] timeout");
3734  return false;
3735  default:
3736  return false;
3737  }
3738  }
3739  return true;
3740 }

3784 bool EveRobotAgent::call_set_task_command_service(
3785  u_char command, std::string target_robot)
3786 {
3787  if (!set_task_command_cli_inner->wait_for_service(std::chrono::milliseconds(200))) {
3788  RCLCPP_ERROR_STREAM(

3790  }

3792  auto req = std::make_shared<task_manager_interfaces::srv::SetTaskCommand::Request>();
3793  req->command = command;
3794  auto inner_client_callback = [&,

3910 void EveRobotAgent::manipulator_init_end_callback(
3911  const std::shared_ptr<eve_server_interfaces::srv::ManiInitEnd::Request> request,
3912  std::shared_ptr<eve_server_interfaces::srv::ManiInitEnd::Response> response)
3913 {
3914  std::lock_guard<std::mutex> lock(service_mutex_);
3915  if (is_control_ != MONITORING) {
3916  response->result = eve_server_interfaces::srv::ManiInitEnd::Response::NOT_MONITORING_MODE;
3917  return;
3918  }
3919 
3920  GcInitEndMotionAction::Goal action_goal;
3921  action_goal.header.stamp = this->now();
3922  action_goal.header.frame_id = "base_footprint";
3923  if (request->motion_name != GcInitEndMotionAction::Goal::INIT_MOTION &&
3924  request->motion_name != GcInitEndMotionAction::Goal::END_MOTION)
3925  {
3926  response->result = eve_server_interfaces::srv::ManiInitEnd::Response::INVALID_MOTION_NAME;
3927  return;
3928  }
3929  action_goal.motion_name = request->motion_name;
3930  action_goal.time_from_start = request->time_from_start;
3931 
3932  // Goal Option 세팅 (Callback 함수)
3933  auto action_goal_options = rclcpp_action::Client<GcInitEndMotionAction>::SendGoalOptions();
3934  action_goal_options.feedback_callback =
3935  std::bind(
3936  &EveRobotAgent::gc_init_end_motion_feedback_callback,
3937  this, std::placeholders::_1, std::placeholders::_2);
3938  action_goal_options.result_callback =
3939  std::bind(&EveRobotAgent::gc_init_end_motion_result_callback, this, std::placeholders::_1);
3940 
3941  // Action 호출합니다.
3942  auto mani_init_end_goal_handle_future =
3943  gc_init_end_motion_action_client_->async_send_goal(action_goal, action_goal_options);
3944  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(this->get_logger(), "[Manipulator Init End] Call async action");
3945 
3946  // Action의 future가 공유상태인지 확인합니다.
3947  if (mani_init_end_goal_handle_future.valid() == false) {
3948  RCLCPP_ERROR_STREAM(this->get_logger(), "[Manipulator Init End] Failed to get action future");
3949  response->result =
3950  eve_server_interfaces::srv::ManiInitEnd::Response::FAIL_TO_GET_ACTION_FUTURE;
3951  return;
3952  }
3953 
3954  // Action의 Goal의 결과가 나오기를 기다립니다.
3955  // 지정된 ROS_TIMEOUT이 경과하거나 결과를 사용할 수 있을 때까지 차단합니다.
3956  // 반환 Value는 결과의 상태를 나타냅니다.
3957  auto future_result = mani_init_end_goal_handle_future.wait_for(std::chrono::milliseconds(500));
3958  if (future_result != std::future_status::ready) {
3959  response->result = eve_server_interfaces::srv::ManiInitEnd::Response::FAIL_TO_SEND_ACTION;
3960  return;
3961  }
3962 
3963  // Action의 Goal response 응답
3964  manipulator_init_end_goal_handle_ = mani_init_end_goal_handle_future.get();
3965  if (!manipulator_init_end_goal_handle_) {
3966  response->result = eve_server_interfaces::srv::ManiInitEnd::Response::ACTION_REJECTED;
3967  return;
3968  }
3969  response->result = eve_server_interfaces::srv::ManiInitEnd::Response::SUCCESS;
