4324 bool EveRobotAgent::call_set_password_srv_inner(std::string password)
4325 {
4326  if (!set_password_cli_inner_->wait_for_service(std::chrono::milliseconds(200))) {
4327  RCLCPP_ERROR_STREAM(get_logger(), "Failed to connect srv server [set_password_cli_inner_]");
4328  }
4329 
4330  auto req = std::make_shared<robotis_server_interfaces::srv::SetPassword::Request>();
4331  req->password = password;
4332  auto inner_client_callback = [&,
4333  this](rclcpp::Client<robotis_server_interfaces::srv::SetPassword>::SharedFuture
4334  inner_future)
4335  {
4336  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(this->get_logger(), "[inner service] callback executed");
4337  auto result = inner_future.get();
4338  auto is_success = result->result;
4339  if (is_success == true) {
4340  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(get_logger(), "Success to set_password");
4341  return true;
4342  } else {
4343  RCLCPP_ERROR_STREAM(get_logger(), "Fail to set_password");
4344  return false;
4345  }
4346  };
4347  auto future = set_password_cli_inner_->async_send_request(req, inner_client_callback);
4348  auto result = future.wait_for(std::chrono::seconds(1));
4349  switch (result) {
4350  case std::future_status::ready:
4351  break;
4352  case std::future_status::timeout:
4353  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(this->get_logger(), "[inner service] timeout");
4354  return false;
4355  default:
4356  return false;
4357  }
4358  return true;
4359 }

4361 void EveRobotAgent::set_password_by_user_callback(
4362  const std::shared_ptr<eve_server_interfaces::srv::SetPassword::Request> request,
4363  std::shared_ptr<eve_server_interfaces::srv::SetPassword::Response> response)
4364 {
4365  // std::lock_guard<std::mutex> lock(service_mutex_);
4366  std::string old_password = request->old_password;
4367  std::string cur_password;
4368  std::string set_password = request->new_password;

4370  if (get_result == true) {

4373  this->get_logger(),
4374  "[] SUCCESS !! (cur_password: " << cur_password << ")");
4375  if (old_password == cur_password) {
4376  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(this->get_logger(), "옛날 비밀번호와 현재 비밀번호 동일함. 성공! ");
4377  bool get_result = call_set_password_srv_inner(set_password);
4378  if (get_result == true) {
4379  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(this->get_logger(), "비밀번호 변경 서비스 최종 성공");
4380  response->status = 0;
4381  response->result = true;
4382  }
4383  } else {

4385  response->status = 1111;
4386  response->result = false;
4387  }

4532 bool EveRobotAgent::call_set_gui_page(std::string page_name, std::string page_info)
4533 {
4534  if (!set_gui_page_cli_->wait_for_service(std::chrono::milliseconds(200))) {
4535  RCLCPP_ERROR_STREAM(get_logger(), "Failed to connect srv server [set_gui_cli]");
4536  }
4537 
4538  auto req = std::make_shared<task_manager_interfaces::srv::SetGUIPage::Request>();
4539  req->page_name = page_name;
4540  bool pub_info = false;
4541  if (page_name == "Info") {
4542  pub_info = true;
4543  }
4544  int choice = -1;
4545  auto inner_client_callback = [&,
4546  this](rclcpp::Client<task_manager_interfaces::srv::SetGUIPage>::SharedFuture
4547  inner_future)
4548  {
4549  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(this->get_logger(), "[inner service] callback executed");
4550  auto result = inner_future.get();
4551  auto is_success = result->result;
4552  if (is_success == true) {
4553  choice = result->result;
4554  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(get_logger(), "Success to set_gui");
4555  if (pub_info == true) {
4556  set_gui_info_data_.data = page_info;
4557  set_gui_info_data_pub_->publish(set_gui_info_data_);
4558  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(get_logger(), "Published page_info");
4559  return true;
4560  }
4561  return true;
4562  } else {
4563  RCLCPP_ERROR_STREAM(get_logger(), "Fail to set_gui");
4564  return false;
4565  }
4566  };
4567  auto future = set_gui_page_cli_->async_send_request(req, inner_client_callback);
4568  auto result = future.wait_for(std::chrono::seconds(1));
4569  while (choice < 0 && rclcpp::ok()) {
4570  std::this_thread::sleep_for(std::chrono::milliseconds(10));
4571  }
4572  switch (result) {
4573  case std::future_status::ready:
4574  break;
4575  case std::future_status::timeout:
4576  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(this->get_logger(), "[inner service] set_gui timeout");
4577  return false;
4578  default:
4579  return false;
4580  }
4581  return true;
4582 }

4620 void EveRobotAgent::pub_monitoring_data()
4621 {
4622  std::lock_guard<std::mutex> lock(mutex_);
4623  auto start_time = now();
4624  auto interval = start_time - last_monitoring_pub_time;
4625  if (fabs(interval.seconds() - 0.2) > 0.02) {
4626  RCLCPP_WARN_STREAM(get_logger(), "Interval : " << interval.seconds());
4627  }
4628 // float cpu_usage;
4629 // float ram_usage;
4630 // check_resource_usage(cpu_usage, ram_usage);
4631  monitoring_data_.header.stamp = now();
4632  monitoring_data_.cpu_usage = ceil(utils.get_current_cpu_usage());
4633 // monitroing_data_. = ceil(utils.get_current_ram_usage());
4634  monitoring_data_.ram_usage = ceil(utils.get_current_ram_usage());
4635  if (error_status_flag_ == true) {
4636  monitoring_data_.robot_status = eve_server_interfaces::msg::MonitoringData::ROBOT_STATUS_ERROR;
4637  } else {
4638  if (monitoring_data_.emergency_status == true) {
4639  // ERROR : 장애
4640  this->monitoring_data_.robot_status =
4641  eve_server_interfaces::msg::MonitoringData::ROBOT_STATUS_ERROR;
4642  } else if (task_list_.tasks.size() != 0) {
4643  if (task_list_.tasks.at(0).task.task_name == "BACK_TO_BASE") {
4644  // RETURNING : 복귀 중
4645  this->monitoring_data_.robot_status =
4646  eve_server_interfaces::msg::MonitoringData::ROBOT_STATUS_RETURNING;
4647  } else {
4648  // PERFORMING_TASK : 태스크 수행 중
4649  this->monitoring_data_.robot_status =
4650  eve_server_interfaces::msg::MonitoringData::ROBOT_STATUS_PERFORMING_TASK;
4651  }
4652  } else {
4653  // READY : 대기 중
4654  this->monitoring_data_.robot_status =
4655  eve_server_interfaces::msg::MonitoringData::ROBOT_STATUS_READY;
4656  }
4657  }
4658  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(get_logger(), "Pub Monitoring Data");
4659  // additional fields 필요시 추가
4660  // if (is_control_ != MONITORING) {
4661  // monitoring_data_.lidar_angle.clear();
4662  // monitoring_data_.lidar_range.clear();
4663  // }
4664  monitoring_data_.maintenance_mode = is_maintenance_mode_;
4665  monitoring_data_pub_->publish(monitoring_data_);
4666  monitoring_data_.detected_door.clear();
4667  if (monitoring_data_.present_task_sequence == "FINISH" &&
4668  monitoring_data_.docked_status == true)
4669  {
4670  this->monitoring_data_.present_task_sequence = "";
4671  }
4672  // auto current_time = now();
4673  // auto dur = current_time - start_time;
4674  // RCLCPP_WARN_STREAM(get_logger(), "Duration : " << dur.seconds());
4675  last_monitoring_pub_time = start_time;

4755 void EveRobotAgent::nav_result_callback(const GoalHandleNavToPose::WrappedResult & result)

4761  struct tm timeinfo;
4762  localtime_r(&raw_time, &timeinfo);
4763  std::strftime(log_time, sizeof(log_time), "%Y%m%d%H%M%S", &timeinfo);

4775  last_navi_uuid_,

4777  log_time, false);

4779  case rclcpp_action::ResultCode::CANCELED:
4780  pub_activity_result(
4781  last_navi_uuid_,
4782  "NavigateTo", "주행 요청이 취소 되었습니다",

4810  last_navi_uuid_,
4811  "NavigateTo", "네비게이션 경로 생성 실패",
4812  log_time, false);
4813  return;
4814  case rclcpp_action::ResultCode::CANCELED:
4815  pub_activity_result(
4816  last_navi_uuid_,
4817  "NavigateTo", "경로 생성 요청 취소됨",
4818  log_time, false);
4819  return;
4820  default:
4821  return;
4822  }
4823 }

4853 bool EveRobotAgent::read_maintenance_mode_file()

4873 bool EveRobotAgent::write_maintenance_mode(bool maintenance_mode)
4874 {
4875  std::lock_guard<std::mutex> lock(mutex_);
4876  try {
4877  std::string mode_file_path = ament_index_cpp::get_package_share_directory(
4878  "eve_robot_agent") +
4879  "/states/mode.yaml";
4880  RCLCPP_ERROR_STREAM(this->get_logger(), "파일 조작 중");
4881  YAML::Emitter yaml_out;
4882  yaml_out << YAML::BeginMap;
4883  yaml_out <<
4884  YAML::Key << "maintenance_mode" <<
4885  YAML::Value << maintenance_mode <<
4886  YAML::EndMap;
4887 
4888  std::ofstream fout(mode_file_path.c_str());
4889  fout << yaml_out.c_str();

4893  log_stream << "Fail to wirte mode data. : " << e.what();
4894  RCLCPP_ERROR_STREAM(this->get_logger(), log_stream.str());
4895  return false;
4896  }
4897  return true;

4901 void EveRobotAgent::update_safety_state()
4902 {
4903  monitoring_data_.brake_source.clear();
4904  if (last_motor_brake_ == true || last_tof_brake_ == true) {
4905  monitoring_data_.safety_state = eve_server_interfaces::msg::MonitoringData::SAFETY_STATE_BREAK;
4906  } else {
4907  monitoring_data_.safety_state =
4908  eve_server_interfaces::msg::MonitoringData::SAFETY_STATE_RUNNING;
4909  }
4910  if (last_motor_brake_ == true) {
4911  monitoring_data_.brake_source.push_back("Bumper");
4912  }
4913  if (last_tof_brake_ == true) {
4914  monitoring_data_.brake_source.push_back("Tof");
4915  }
4916 }

4919 void EveRobotAgent::run_maintenance_mode_check()
4920 {
4921  while (is_maintenance_mode_check_running_) {
4922  is_maintenance_mode_enabled();
4923  std::cout << "run!" << std::endl;
4924  std::this_thread::sleep_for(std::chrono::seconds(1));
4925  }
4926 }
4927 
4928 void EveRobotAgent::start_maintenance_check()
4929 {
4930  is_maintenance_mode_check_running_ = true;
4931  // Store the future returned by std::async
4932  maintenance_future_ = std::async(
4933  std::launch::async, &EveRobotAgent::run_maintenance_mode_check,
4934  this);
4935 }
4936 
4937 
4938 void EveRobotAgent::stop_maintenance_check()
4939 {
4940  is_maintenance_mode_check_running_ = false;
4941  // Wait for the asynchronous task to complete (if it's still running)
4942  if (maintenance_future_.valid()) {
4943  maintenance_future_.wait();
4944  }
4945 }

4947 void EveRobotAgent::is_maintenance_mode_enabled()
4948 {
4949 // std::cout << "check resource launch!" << std::endl;
4950  bool maintenance_mode = read_maintenance_mode_file();
4951  std::lock_guard<std::mutex> lock(status_check_mutex_);
4952  if (is_maintenance_mode_ != maintenance_mode) {
4953  is_maintenance_mode_ = maintenance_mode;
4954  RCLCPP_WARN_STREAM(get_logger(), "Mode Changed!");
4955  if (is_maintenance_mode_ == true) {
4956  write_pub_agent_log(
4957  "점검 시작", eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_LOW,
4958  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::TYPE_INFO);
4959  is_maintenance_mode_ = true;
4960  } else {
4961  write_pub_agent_log(
4962  "점검 종료", eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::LEVEL_LOW,
4963  eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log::TYPE_INFO);
4964  is_maintenance_mode_ = false;
4965  }
4966  }
4967 }

4969 void EveRobotAgent::write_pub_agent_log(std::string command, signed char level, signed char type)

4972  log.contents = command;
4973  log.source = "EveRobotAgent";

4976  write_log_file(log);
4977  RCLCPP_ERROR_STREAM(this->get_logger(), "log write");
4978 // eve_server_interfaces::msg::Log server_log;
4979  publish_log(command, level, type);
4980  RCLCPP_ERROR_STREAM(this->get_logger(), "server log pub");
4981 }

4983 
4984 void EveRobotAgent::write_log_file(aimbot_log_interfaces::msg::Log log)
4985 {
4986  auto log_stream_ptr = std::make_shared<std::ofstream>();
4987 
4988  try {
4989  // Get the current time
4990  rclcpp::Time ros_time = this->now();
4991  time_t now = ros_time.seconds();
4992  struct tm tstruct;
4993  localtime_r(&now, &tstruct);
4994 
4995  char time_buf[100];
4996  strftime(time_buf, sizeof(time_buf), "%Y-%m-%d", &tstruct); // YYYY-MM-DD
4997  std::string file_name = default_file_path + "/" + time_buf + ".csv";
4998 
4999  bool file_exist_flag = (access(file_name.c_str(), F_OK) != -1);
5000  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(get_logger(), "save_path : " << file_name.c_str());
5001  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(get_logger(), (file_exist_flag ? "File is exist" : "Make a new file"));
5002 
5003  log_stream_ptr->open(file_name, std::ofstream::out | std::ofstream::app);
5004 
5005  if (file_exist_flag == false) {
5006  *log_stream_ptr <<
5007  "Data,Time,UNIX Time,Level,Type,Source,Contents,Current Floor,Current Position," <<
5008  "Target POI,Battery Status,Battery Voltage,Capture\n";
5009  }
5010 
5011  char log_time[50];
5012  std::strftime(log_time, sizeof(log_time), "%Y-%m-%d,%H:%M:%S", &tstruct);
5013  double ms =
5014  (ros_time.seconds() - static_cast<double>(static_cast<int>(ros_time.seconds()))) * 1000.0;
5015 
5016  std::string level;
5017  switch (log.level) {
5018  case log.LEVEL_HIGH: level = "HIGH"; break;
5019  case log.LEVEL_MEDIUM: level = "MEDIUM"; break;
5020  case log.LEVEL_LOW: level = "LOW"; break;
5021  case log.LEVEL_DEBUG: level = "DEBUG"; break;
5022  }
5023 
5024  std::string type;
5025  switch (log.type) {
5026  case log.TYPE_INFO: type = "INFO"; break;
5027  case log.TYPE_WARN: type = "WARN"; break;
5028  case log.TYPE_ERROR: type = "ERROR"; break;
5029  }
5030 
5031  uint32_t precisionVal = 2;
5032  std::string current_position =
5033  "x: " +
5034  std::to_string(monitoring_data_.pose_from_map_current.x).substr(
5035  0,
5036  std::to_string(monitoring_data_.pose_from_map_current.x).find(".") + precisionVal + 1) + "/" +
5037  "y: " +
5038  std::to_string(monitoring_data_.pose_from_map_current.y).substr(
5039  0,
5040  std::to_string(monitoring_data_.pose_from_map_current.y).find(".") + precisionVal + 1) + "/" +
5041  "theta: " +
5042  std::to_string(monitoring_data_.pose_from_map_current.theta * (180.0 / M_PI)).substr(
5043  0, std::to_string(
5044  monitoring_data_.pose_from_map_current.theta * (180.0 / M_PI)).find(".") + precisionVal +
5045  1);
5046 
5047  *log_stream_ptr << log_time << "." <<
5048  std::dec << std::setw(3) << std::setfill('0') << static_cast<int>(ms) << "," <<
5049  std::fixed << std::setprecision(6) << ros_time.seconds() << "," <<
5050  level << "," << type << "," <<
5051  log.source << "," << log.contents << "," << monitoring_data_.area_id << "," <<
5052  current_position << "," << log.target_poi << "," << battery_status_ << "," <<
5053  battery_state_data_.voltage;
5054 
5055  if (log.capture == true && capture_ && compressed_image_msg_.data.size()) {
5056  char log_time[30];
5057  {
5058  std::time_t raw_time = static_cast<time_t>(compressed_image_msg_.header.stamp.sec);
5059  struct tm timeinfo;
5060  localtime_r(&raw_time, &timeinfo);
5061  std::strftime(log_time, sizeof(log_time), "%Y-%m-%d-%H-%M-%S", &timeinfo);
5062  }
5063 
5064  std::string file_name = default_cap_file_path + "/" + log_time + ".jpg";
5065  *log_stream_ptr << "," <<
5066  (save_image(file_name) ? std::string(log_time) + ".jpg" : "failure");
5067 
5068  } else if (log.capture == true && capture_) {
5069  *log_stream_ptr << "," << "NO IMAGE";
5070  }
5071 
5072  *log_stream_ptr << "\n";
5073 
5074  log_stream_ptr->close();
5075  log_stream_ptr.reset();
5076  } catch (std::exception & ex) {
5077  RCLCPP_ERROR_STREAM(get_logger(), "[Aimbot Log] " << ex.what());
5078  if (log_stream_ptr != nullptr) {
5079  log_stream_ptr->close();
5080  log_stream_ptr.reset();
5081  }
5082  }
5083 }

5085 std::string EveRobotAgent::convert_ros_time_to_utc(const builtin_interfaces::msg::Time & ros_time)
5086 {
5087  std::chrono::system_clock::time_point utc_tp = std::chrono::system_clock::time_point(
5088  std::chrono::seconds(ros_time.sec) + std::chrono::nanoseconds(ros_time.nanosec)
5089  );
5090 
5091  std::time_t time_t_utc = std::chrono::system_clock::to_time_t(utc_tp);
5092  std::tm tm_utc = *std::gmtime(&time_t_utc);
5093 
5094  std::ostringstream utc_stream;
5095  utc_stream << std::put_time(&tm_utc, "%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%SZ");
5096 
5097  return utc_stream.str();
5098 }

5100 
5101 bool EveRobotAgent::save_image(std::string file_name)
5102 {
5103  std::lock_guard<std::mutex> lock(service_mutex_);
5104  cv_bridge::CvImagePtr cv_ptr;
5105  try {
5106  cv_ptr = cv_bridge::toCvCopy(compressed_image_msg_, sensor_msgs::image_encodings::BGR8);
5107  } catch (cv_bridge::Exception & e) {
5108  RCLCPP_ERROR_STREAM(get_logger(), "cv_bridge exception: " << e.what());
5109  return false;
5110  }
5111 
5112  std::vector<int> compression_params;
5113  compression_params.push_back(cv::IMWRITE_JPEG_QUALITY);
5114  compression_params.push_back(10);
5115 
5116  try {
5117  cv::imwrite(file_name.c_str(), cv_ptr->image, compression_params);
5118  RCLCPP_INFO_STREAM(get_logger(), "Save the image : " << file_name);
5119  } catch (std::runtime_error & ex) {
5120  RCLCPP_ERROR_STREAM(get_logger(), "Failed to save the image");
5121  return false;
5122  }
5123  return true;
5124 }

5127 int main(int argc, char ** argv)
5128 {
5129  // force flush of the stdout buffer.
5130  // this ensures a correct sync of all prints
5131  // even when executed simultaneously within the launch file.
5132  setvbuf(stdout, nullptr, _IONBF, BUFSIZ);
5133 
5134  rclcpp::init(argc, argv);
5135  rclcpp::executors::MultiThreadedExecutor executor(rclcpp::ExecutorOptions(), 4);
5136  // make nodehandle
5137  auto nh = std::make_shared<eve_robot_agent::EveRobotAgent>();
5138  // add to the executor
5139  executor.add_node(nh);
5140  executor.spin();
5141 
5142  rclcpp::shutdown();
5143  return 0;
5144 }
